oses%20a%201.2%25%20increase%20in%20the%20outlay%20for%20the%20department%20of%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20a%200.7%25%20increase%20in%20the%20outlay%20for%20health%20research%2C%20and%20a%2016%25%20dip%20in%20funds%20for%20the%20biotechnology%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20increase%20below%20the%20rate%20of%20inflation%20is%20effectively%20a%20decrease%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ayan%20Banerjee%2C%20professor%20of%20physics%20at%20IISER%20Calcutta%2C%20told%20the%20daily.%20%E2%80%9CGiven%20these%20trends%2C%20where%20is%20the%20corpus%20money%20going%20to%20come%20from%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Gokhale%2C%20secretary%20in%20the%20department%20of%20biotechnology%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20outlay%20for%20biotechnology%20had%20decreased%20because%20certain%20COVID-related%20initiatives%20had%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20budget%2C%20the%20government%20had%20proposed%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20National%20Research%20Foundation%20(NRF)%20in%20alignment%20with%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20with%20a%20budget%20allocation%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore.%20However%2C%20the%20specifics%20of%20this%20proposal%20remain%20unclear%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1967353%5C%22%3Ehad%20declared%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20would%20serve%20as%20the%20ex-officio%20president%20of%20the%20NRF%20board%2C%20given%20the%20broad-ranging%20scope%20of%20the%20body%20that%20has%20implications%20for%20all%20ministries.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20science%20and%20technology%20and%20education%20will%20hold%20ex-officio%20positions%20as%20vice-presidents%20of%20the%20NRF.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20and%20researchers%20expressed%20conc