o%20local-level%20politicians%20are%20forcefully%20stopping%20the%20on-going%20works%2C%20using%20physical%20violence%20against%20and%20extorting%20money%20from%20the%20contractor%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20sent%20to%20Shinde%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Contractors%20Association%20(MSCA)%20and%20State%20Engineers%20Association%20(SEA)%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20groups%20cannot%20be%20controlled%20by%20government%20officials.%20Increased%20instances%20of%20threatening%20with%20physical%20violence%3B%20beating%20up%20the%20contractor%20if%20they%20registered%20an%20opposition%20and%20dictating%20their%20own%20orders%20are%20growing%20across%20the%20state.%20These%20groups%20are%20working%20in%20an%20identical%20manner%20all%20over%2C%20where%20they%20file%20written%20complaints%20against%20the%20contractor%20and%20later%20demand%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20ruling%20MLAs%2C%20MPs%20and%20other%20elected%20representatives%20have%20managed%20to%20get%20sanction%20for%20huge%20amounts%20of%20developmental%20works%20in%20the%20state.%20While%20executing%20it%2C%20political%20groups%20who%20are%20in%20the%20Opposition%20are%20ensuring%20that%20the%20works%20are%20stopped.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20these%20groups%20are%20ganging%20up%20against%20the%20contractors%20and%20the%20labourers%2C%20and%20abusing%20as%20well%20as%20beating%20them%20to%20stop%20the%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20is%20dated%20February%206%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilind%20Bhosle%2C%20who%20is%20president%20of%20both%20the%20MSCA%20and%20SEA%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20state%20government%20has%20issued%20orders%20for%20works%20up%20to%20Rs%20one%20lakh%20crore%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9COur%20contractors%20are%20facing%20trouble%20on%20ground%20during%20