%20but%20Powell%20did%20not%20explicitly%20state%20a%20timeline.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20interview%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Fed%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdid-federal-reserve-cut-interest-rates-continue-pause-inflation-recession-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%3C%2Fa%3E's%20December%202023%20forecasts%20for%20three%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20this%20year%20remain%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20participants%20in%20a%20meeting%20held%20by%20the%20Federal%20Open%20Market%20Committee%20predicted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finterest-rates-fed-pauses-increases-december-rate-cuts-powell-inflation-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20cuts%20for%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bringing%20interest%20rates%20down%20to%204.6%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20told%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20correspondent%20Scott%20Pelley%20that%20those%20forecasts%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20say%2C%20though%2C%20nothing%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20meantime%20that%20would%20lead%20me%20to%20think%20that%20people%20would%20dramatically%20change%20their%20forecasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said%20when%20asked%20if%20the%20cuts%20to%204.6%25%20are%20still%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%20did%20not%20explicitly%20provide%20a%20timeline%2C%20but%20Pelley%20noted%20during%20the%20broadcast%20that%20the%20first%20cut%20could%20come%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20of%20the%20year%2C%20few%20months%20before%20the%20election%26quot%3B%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Associated%20Press%20reported%20that%20most%20economists%20have%20predicted%20that%20the%20cuts%20can%20come%20as%20early%20as%20May%20or%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-fed-interest-rate-cut-outlook-inflation-bank-of-america-2024-2%5C%22%20targe