g%20to%20lower%20interest%20rates%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20maybe%20getting%20people%20elected.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Powell%20insisted%20during%20the%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20interview%20that%20the%20Fed's%20decisions%20are%20apolitical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20consider%20politics%20in%20our%20decisions.%20We%20never%20do.%20And%20we%20never%20will%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bintegrity%20is%20priceless.%20And%20at%20the%20end%2C%20that's%20all%20you%20have.%20And%20we%20plan%20on%20keeping%20ours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-60-minutes-interview-fed-interest-rate-cuts-before-election-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707098553000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c038846fcb546d2d4bf452%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-60-minutes-interview-fed-interest-rate-cuts-before-election-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Fed%20forecast%20in%20December%20there%20would%20be%20three%20interest%20rate%20cuts%20in%202024.%20Fed%20Chair%20Powell%20said%20in%20a%20%26quot%3B60%20Minutes%26quot%3B%20interview%20that%20nothing%20has%20changed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-60-minutes-interview-fed-interest-rate-cuts-before-election-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22El%20Salvador's%20President%20Bukele%20claims%20election%20victory%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707098152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F17EAC%2Fproduction%2F_132546979_mediaitem132546145.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-681