21109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kitchen%20and%20staircase%20on%20the%20first%20floor.%3Cp%3EBen%2FLife%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20destroying%20his%20crop%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20give%20the%20farmer%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20have%20to%20do%20this%2C%20but%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20should%20because%20we%20were%20coming%20into%20a%20new%20area%2C%20a%20new%20culture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20delay%20in%20getting%20the%20project%20started%2C%20the%20construction%20process%20was%20also%20held%20up%20by%20two%20especially%20bad%20monsoon%20seasons%2C%20Ben%20said.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiahighlights.com%2Fthailand%2Frainy-season%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonsoon%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20place%20from%20May%20to%20October%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221479%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dining%20area.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b208ca617029e90a604105%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221109%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20dining%20area.%3Cp%3EBen%2FLife%20in%20Thailand%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20whole%20land%20was%20flooded%2C%20which%20meant%20the%20builders%20had%20no%20access%20to%20the%20site.%20When%20the%20water%20subsided%2C%20it%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20access%20road%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20another%20two%20months%20before%20the%20government%20rebuilt%20the%20road%20so%20the%20builders%20could%20get%20back%20to%20the%20house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20built%20in%20seven%20months%2C%20was%20only%20completed%20after%2022%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22htt