Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProblems%20along%20the%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Venezuelan%20national%2C%20I%20am%20only%20allowed%20in%20the%20Schengen%20Area%20for%20three%20months%20at%20a%20time.%20This%20means%20that%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20staying%20in%20Europe%2C%20I%20have%20to%20travel%20to%20non-Schengen%20countries%20like%20Romania%20or%20Bulgaria%20every%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20sites%20like%20Worldpackers%20and%20Workaway%20to%20find%20my%20jobs.%20One%20time%2C%20the%20only%20available%20job%20outside%20the%20Schengen%20zone%20was%20in%20Sofia%2C%20Bulgaria.%20I%20had%20to%20live%20with%20and%20help%20an%20old%20man%20who%20was%20partly%20disabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20week%20was%20amazing.%20But%20he%20turned%20rude%20and%20grumpy%2C%20making%20fun%20of%20my%20Latin%20Spanish%20and%20saying%20it%20was%20not%20the%20right%20way%20to%20speak%20the%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20living%20arrangement%20made%20me%20uncomfortable%20too%20%E2%80%93%20I%20was%20sleeping%20on%20a%20mattress%20basically%20next%20to%20him.%20He%20was%20also%20an%20artist%20who%20painted%20nude%20women%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20model%20for%20him.%20I%20was%20there%20for%20three%20weeks%20before%20I%20tried%20to%20find%20a%20different%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20happy%20end%20to%20that%20story%20was%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20find%20a%20friendly%20host%20family%20in%20another%20city%20in%20Bulgaria%2C%20and%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20only%20job%20I%20accepted%20without%20a%20video%20call%2C%20so%20I%20am%20always%20careful%20to%20call%20the%20host%20and%20ask%20for%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20accommodation%20now.%20I%20also%20make%20sure%20to%20have%20two%20or%20three%20options%20in%20each%20city%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20it's%20the%20only%20place%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20mindset%20that%20has%20helped%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%