khar-sharma-company-124020400647_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Crucial%20Jharkhand%20Floor%20Test%20Today%3A%20Who%20Has%20The%20Numbers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESome%2040%20MLAs%20of%20the%20ruling%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20and%20its%20alliance%20partners%20returned%20to%20Ranchi%20from%20Hyderabad%20late%20Sunday%20evening%20to%20attend%20the%20floor%20test%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20were%20kept%20in%20a%20resort%20near%20Hyderabad%20after%20JMM%20leader%20Champai%20Soren%20was%20appointed%20Chief%20Minister.%20His%20predecessor%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20the%20son%20of%20JMM%20co-founder%20Shibu%20Soren%2C%20is%20in%20jail%20in%20an%20alleged%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20JMM%20took%20the%20'resort%20politics'%20route%20to%20prevent%20its%20MLAs%20from%20being%20'approached'%20by%20rival%20parties%20for%20switching%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20alliance%20in%20Jharkhand%20has%20five%20more%20MLAs%20from%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2041%20in%20the%2081-member%20assembly.%20One%20of%20the%2081%20seats%20is%20vacant%2C%20hence%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2041%20when%20counted%20for%2080%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMM%2C%20Congress%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(ML)%20have%20a%20total%20of%2046%20MLAs.%20These%20are%20JMM%20(28)%2C%20Congress%20(16)%2C%20RJD%20(1)%2C%20and%20CPI(ML)%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20allies%20have%2029%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnless%20something%20drastic%20or%20a%20big%20twist%20happens%2C%20the%20JMM%20government%20will%20sail%20through%20the%20floor%20test%2C%20political%20analysts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20the%20JMM%20is%20facing%20a%20floor%20test.%20In%20September%202022%2C%20Hemant%20Soren's%20government%20won%20a%20majority%20test%20with%2048%20votes%20in%20his%20favour.%20Then%20too%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%20faced%20a%20threat%20of%20disq