%20concern.%20The%20leaders%20have%20been%20insisting%20they%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20form%20government%20even%20before%20t7he%20arrest%20of%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20which%20took%20place%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20submitted%20the%20report%20(to%20the%20Governor)%20with%2043%20MLAs%20in%20our%20support.%20We%20expect%20the%20number%20will%20reach%2046-47...%20so%20there%20is%20no%20problem.%20Our%20'gathbandhan'%2C%20or%20alliance%2C%20is%20very%20strong%2C%26quot%3B%20Champai%20Soren%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20buzz%20that%20two%20JMM%20MLAs%20can%20skip%20the%20voting%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20majority%20mark.%20The%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20are%20due%20in%20October-November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20political%20crisis%20in%20Jharkhand%20started%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20a%20land%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707061260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fqohc3vk_jharkhand-mlas_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-mlas-on-way-back-ahead-of-tomorrows-floor-test-4992590%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20MLAs%20of%20Jharkhand's%20ruling%20JMM-Congress-RJD%20alliance%20were%20taken%20from%20Hyderabad%20to%20Ranchi%20ahead%20of%20tomorrow's%20crucial%20floor%20test%20of%20the%20Champai%20Soren%20government.%20The%20MLAs%20were%20shifted%20to%20Hyderabad%20following%20concerns%20over%20possible%20Operation%20Lotus%20b%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-mlas-on-way-back-ahead-of-tomorrows-floor-test-4992590%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-mlas-on-way-back-ahead-of-tomorrows-floor-test-4992590%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-mlas-on-way-back-ahead-of-tomorrows-floor-test-4992590%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20Stars%20On%20Confrontation%20Path%20With%20PCB.%20Report%20Claims%20Reason%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20discord%20is%20brewing%20between%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20and%20the%20players%20who%20are%20unhappy%20at%20not%20having%20their%20NOCs%20extended%20for%20league%20appearances%20through%20this%20month.%20A%20well-informed%20source%20in%20the%20PCB%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20some%20players%20were%20upset%20over%20the%20inconsistent%20policies%20of%20the%20board%20while%20granting%20NOCs%20to%20players%20to%20play%20in%20foreign%20leagues.%20The%20players%20who%20are%20presently%20engaged%20in%20the%20ILT20%20and%20the%20Bangladesh%20Premier%20League%20(BPL%202024)%20had%20requested%20the%20PCB%20to%20extend%20their%20NOCs%20so%20that%20they%20could%20complete%20their%20assignments%20before%20returning%20home%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20Super%20League%20(PSL)%20which%20begins%20on%20February%2017.%20But%20the%20PCB%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20the%20players%20that%20their%20NOCs%20would%20not%20be%20extended%20and%20they%20had%20to%20return%20as%20per%20the%20original%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20there%20are%20different%20conditions%20and%20return%20dates%20given%20to%20the%20players%20which%20has%20caused%20the%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20majority%20of%20players%20have%20to%20return%20by%20February%207%2C%20there%20are%20some%20players%20who%20can%20return%20on%2011th%20and%20some%20even%20on%2016th%20and%20this%20is%20causing%20frustration%20among%20the%20players%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%2C%20Babar%20Azam%2C%20Saim%20Ayub%2C%20Muhammad%20Nawaz%2C%20Haris%20Rauf%2C%20Usama%20Mir%2C%20Shadab%20Khan%20Aamer%20Jamal%20Azam%20Khan%2C%20Imad%20Wasim%2C%20Muhammad%20Amir%2C%20Muhammad%20Hasnain%2C%20Ahmed%20Shehzad%20and%20Shoaib%20Malik%20are%20some%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20players%20busy%20in%20the%20two%20leagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20players%20had%20asked%20the%20PCB%20for%20extension%20in%20their%20respective%20leagues%20as%20the%20PSL%20would%20not%20begin%20before%20February%2017%2C%20but%20the%20home%20board%20was%20not%20relenting%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20return%20for%20pre-PSL%20activities%20with%20their%20respective%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20instructed%20both%20its%20centrally%20contracted%20players%20and%20those%20without%20contracts%20to%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707061080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjaks83k8_pakistan-cricket-team-afp_625x300_17_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-stars-on-confrontation-path-with-pcb-report-claims-reason-is-4992512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20severe%20discord%20is%20brewing%20between%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20and%20the%20players%20who%20are%20unhappy%20at%20not%20having%20their%20NOCs%20extended%20for%20league%20appearances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Muslims%20Can%20Adopt%20Without%20Declaring%20Under%20Shariat%20Law%2C%20Says%20Delhi%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Delhi%20court%2C%20dismissing%20a%20partition%20suit%2C%20held%20that%20any%20individual%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20can%20adopt%20a%20child%20without%20making%20a%20declaration%20under%20the%20Shariat%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20ruling%2C%20any%20such%20adoption%20shall%20be%20governed%20by%20the%20general%20law%20and%20not%20by%20the%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law.%20The%20said%20child%20would%20become%20the%20legitimate%20child%20of%20his%20adoptive%20parents%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20partition%20suit%20filed%20by%20the%20brother%20of%20one%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20-%20who%20has%20died%20-%20seeking%20a%20share%20in%20his%20property%2C%20leaving%20one-fourth%20share%20for%20Mr%20Ahmed's%20widow%20as%20the%20couple%20had%20no%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20and%20his%20wife%20Gulzaro%20Begam%20adopted%20a%20son%20-%20Abdul%20Samad%20alias%20Sameer%20-%20without%20making%20any%20declaration%20under%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Sessions%20Judge%20(ADJ)%20Parveen%20Singh%20held%20that%20even%20under%20the%20prevalent%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20Shariat%2C%20a%20Muslim%20who%20has%20not%20filed%20a%20declaration%20under%20section%203%20of%20the%20Shariat%20Act%20can%20adopt%20a%20child%20and%20the%20said%20child%20would%20become%20the%20legitimate%20child%20of%20his%20adoptive%20parents%20with%20all%20rights%2C%20privileges%2C%20and%20responsibilities%20that%20are%20attached%20to%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApplying%20this%20principle%20to%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20present%20case%2C%20I%20find%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20or%20even%20an%20assertion%20that%20deceased%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20had%20filed%20any%20declaration%20under%20section%203%20of%20the%20Shariat%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20ADJ%20Parveen%20Singh%20said%20in%20the%20judgment%20dated%20February%203%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20deceased%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20had%20elected%20not%20to%20be%20governed%20by%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20on%20the%20subject%20of%20adoption%20and%20thus%2C%20if%20he%20had%20adopted%20a%20child%20as%20claimed%20by%20defendant%20no.%201%20(Gulzaro%20Begam)%2C%20the%20said%20adoption%20shall%20be%20governed%20by%20general%20law%20of%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20passing%20the%20judgment%2C%20the%20additional%20district%20judge%20also%20discussed%20a%20previous%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20that%20a%20Muslim%20who%20has%20not%20filed%20any%20declaration%20under%20section%203%20of%20the%20Shariat%20Act%2C%20shall%20not%20be%20governed%20by%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%2FShariat%20on%20the%20subjects%20of%20adoption%2C%20wills%2C%20and%20legacies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%20in%20the%20case%20of%20such%20a%20person%2C%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20cannot%20be%20applied%20to%20these%20subjects.%20That%20being%20the%20case%2C%20these%20judgments%20shall%20only%20be%20applicable%20to%20the%20case%20of%20Muslims%20who%20have%20filed%20a%20declaration%20under%20section%203%20of%20the%20Shariat%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partition%20suit%20filed%20by%20Zamir%20Ahmed's%20brother%20Iqbal%20Ahmed%20sought%20a%20decree%20per%20Muslim%20Law.%20Zamir%20Ahmed's%20widow%20and%20his%20other%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20were%20made%20defendants%20in%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20claimed%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20died%20without%20a%20child%20on%20July%203%2C%202008.%20The%20suit%20said%20that%20being%20a%20Muslim%2C%20the%20inheritance%20of%20the%20property%20of%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20is%20to%20be%20governed%20by%20Shariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiff%20claimed%20that%20Zamir%20Ahmed's%20widow%20was%20entitled%20to%20a%20one-fourth%20share%20in%20the%20properties%20left%20behind%20by%20him%2C%20his%20three%20sisters%20were%20entitled%20to%20a%2015%20per%20cent%20share%20in%20the%20properties%20left%20behind%2C%20and%20the%20remaining%2060%20per%20cent%20devolved%20upon%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20Zamir%20Ahmed's%20other%20five%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20widow%20and%20a%20son%2C%20his%20inheritance%20is%20accordingly%20to%20be%20decided%20in%20this%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Muslim%20Law%20of%20Inheritance%2C%20there%20are%20three%20classes%20of%20legal%20heirs%3A%20sharers%2C%20residuary%2C%20and%20distant%20kindred.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20of%20the%2012%20Quranic%20sharers%2C%20only%20the%20widow%20of%20the%20deceased%20is%20surviving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20of%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20defendant%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20was%20that%20as%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20had%20no%20son%2C%20his%20widow%20is%20entitled%20to%20a%20one-fourth%20share%20in%20his%20estate%20and%2C%20they%20being%20Mr%20Ahmed's%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20would%20have%20the%20remaining%20share%20where%20the%20brothers%20will%20get%20double%20the%20sisters'%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20rejected%20the%20claim%20that%20said%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20the%20defendants%20could%20only%20have%20inherited%20from%20the%20estate%20of%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20had%20there%20been%20no%20son%20to%20claim%20the%20residuary%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20it%20has%20been%20held%20that%20Zamir%20Ahmed%20had%20a%20son%20he%20had%20adopted%20and%20the%20said%20son%20has%20the%20same%20status%20as%20a%20biological%20son%20and%20has%20all%20the%20rights%2C%20privileges%2C%20and%20responsibilities%20attached%20to%20that%20relationship.%20For%20inheritance%2C%20the%20said%20son%20has%20to%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20son%20being%20a%20residuary%20excludes%20the%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20of%20deceased%20Zamir%20Ahmed.%20This%20being%20the%20case%2C%20I%20am%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20the%20defendant%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20are%20not%20entitled%20to%20the%20partition%20as%20prayed%20for.%20The%20issue%20is%20accordingly%20decided%2C%26quot%3B%20ADJ%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20