he%20flight%20attendant%20does%20little%20to%20ease%20the%20traumas%20of%20such%20scenarios%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20at%20the%20beginning%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20pros%20of%20his%20job%2C%20the%20flight%20attendant%20threw%20light%20on%20travel%20benefits%2C%20healthcare%20benefits%2C%20going%20to%20different%20cities%20and%20experiencing%20something%20different%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20staying%20away%20from%20home%20for%20three%20days%20at%20a%20time%20and%20dealing%20with%20mean%20passengers%20was%20the%20biggest%20cons%20as%20per%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20a%20good%20relationship%20with%20your%20spouse.%20You%20will%20miss%20events%2C%20holidays%2C%20etc%20but%20it%20depends%20on%20how%20you%20work%20it%20out%2C%20if%20there%20are%20young%20kids%20in%20the%20family%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20come%20with%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDepends%20on%20the%20airline%20but%20typically%20starting%20pay%20is%20around%20%2424%2Fflight%20hour.%20That%20doesn't%20include%20per%20diem%2C%20some%20pay%20more%20if%20flights%20are%20full%20or%20close%20to%20full%2C%20what%20position%20you%20fly%2C%20etc.%20top%20out%20pay%20is%20after%20about%2015%20years%20and%20then%20it's%20about%20%2475%2Fflight%20hour%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20flight%20attendant%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20passenger%20can%20do%20that%20would%20make%20your%20job%20easier%20%2F%20stress-free%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20user%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHonestly%2C%20just%20be%20nice.%20Say%20hi%20and%20ask%20how%20our%C2%A0day%20is.%20It's%20the%20simple%20things....oh%20and%20chocolate%20works%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707056220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2Fd3f7ph28_flight-generic_625x300_05_September_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22http