0the%20handling%20of%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20leaders%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20government%2C%20and%20my%20party%20that%20ahead%20of%20the%20OBC%20Elgar%20rally%20held%20in%20Ambad%20on%20November%2017%2C%20I%20resigned%20from%20the%20cabinet%20on%20November%2016%20and%20then%20went%20to%20attend%20that%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20need%20for%20sacking.%20I%20have%20tendered%20my%20resignation.%20I%20will%20fight%20for%20the%20OBCs%20till%20the%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20kept%20quiet%20for%20more%20than%20two%20months%20because%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Deputy%C2%A0%20CM%20asked%20him%20not%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhujbal%20reiterated%20that%20he%20was%20not%20opposed%20to%20Marathas%20getting%20the%20reservation%20but%20is%20against%20sharing%20the%20existing%20quota%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20chief%20minister%20will%20be%20able%20to%20clarify%2C%20but%20I%20can%20only%20say%20as%20of%20now%20that%20Bhujbal's%20resignation%20has%20not%20been%20accepted%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sanjay%20Raut%20sought%20to%20know%20who%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20accept%20Bhujbal's%20resignation%20-%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20or%20Deputy%20CM%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20precedent%20that%20those%20who%20oppose%20the%20chief%20minister%20or%20the%20government%20have%20no%20right%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20all%20communities%20should%20get%20their%20rights%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20encroaching%20on%20others'%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20Raut%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20even%20Mr%20Bhujbal%20says%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20at%20Antarwali%20Sarati%20village%20in%20Jalna%20district%2C%20Jarange%20rubbished%20Bhujbal's%20allegations%20that%20fake%20and%20overwritten%20records%20were%20being%20used%20to%20get%20the%20reservation%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Bhujbal)%20doesn't%20understand%20anything.%20There%20is%20a%20law%2C%20a%20government%2C%20a%20committee%20and%20scholars%20working%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20but%20Bhujbal%20doubts%20his%20own%20government.%20He%20is%20trying%20to%20damage%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20activist%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20become%20Mr%20Bhujbal's%20business%20to%20damage%20every%20party%20he%20joins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20he%20(Bhujbal)%20wants%20to%20resign%2C%20he%20should%20do%20it%2C%20but%20should%20not%20talk%20against%20Maratha%20reservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jarange%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707054300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fpl87f72c_devendra-fadnavis-650_625x300_03_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-clarification-after-maharashtra-mla-chhagan-bhujbal-says-resigned-in-november-4993002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20disclosure%20by%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20that%20he%20resigned%20as%20a%20minister%20last%20November%20has%20put%20a%20focus%20on%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20tightrope%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20government%20is%20walking%20amid%20restlessness%20in%20OBCs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-clarificatio