jput.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESridevi%20died%20in%20Dubai%20in%20February%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Sridevi's%20death%2C%20she%20made%20sensational%20claims%2C%20including%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoverup%20between%20the%20two%20governments%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20based%20on%20her%20%26quot%3Binvestigations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20PTI%20query%2C%20Ms%20Pinniti%20expressed%20disbelief%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20CBI%20has%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20me%20without%20recording%20my%20statement...%20Moreover%2C%20the%20evidence%20will%20be%20given%20to%20court%20when%20charges%20are%20framed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20letters%20in%20question%20are%20incriminating%20against%20the%20very%20authorities%20under%20whom%20the%20CBI%20comes%2C%20CBI%20becomes%20a%20party%20of%20conflict%20to%20be%20the%20entity%20to%20collect%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20filing%20an%20FIR%20against%20her%20last%20year%2C%20the%20CBI%20conducted%20searches%20at%20her%20residence%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20on%20December%202%2C%20seizing%20digital%20devices%2C%20including%20phones%20and%20laptops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CBI%20report%20before%20a%20special%20court%2C%20the%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20documents%20presented%20by%20her%20during%20YouTube%20discussions%2C%20pertaining%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20the%20Defence%20Minister%2C%20were%20%26quot%3Bforged%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20her%20and%20Mr%20Kamath%20under%20relevant%20Sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%2C%20including%20for%20criminal%20conspiracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20suspect%20Deepti%20Rani%20Pinniti%20has%20time%20and%20again%20maligned%20the%20image%20of%20the%20present%20government%20by%20bizarrely%20accusing%20the%20government%20as%20the%20sponsor%20of%20the%20death%20of%20Sridevi...%2C%26quot%3B%20Mumbai-based%20lawyer%20Chandni%20Shah%20alleged%20in%20her%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707052860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fsef4p5po_sridevi_625x300_20_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-cited-forged-letters-from-pm-ministers-on-sridevi-death-cbi-4992811%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBI%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20a%20self-styled%20investigator%20alleging%20she%20cited%20%26quot%3Bforged%26quot%3B%20letters%20from%20high%20dignitaries%2C%20including%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20in%20a%20YouTube%20video%20to%20support%20her%20claims%20about%20Sridevi's%20death%2C%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-cited-forged-letters-from-pm-ministers-on-sridevi-death-cbi-4992811%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-cited-forged-letters-from-pm-ministers-on-sridevi-death-cbi-4992811%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fyoutuber-cited-forged-letters-from-pm-ministers-on-sridevi-death-cbi-4992811%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Religiosity%20Conundrum%20and%20its%20Resolution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162930%2FIMG_2541.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20events%20of%20national%20importance%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20quick%20chronological%20succession.%20I%20wish%20to%20examine%20their%20inter-connections%20in%20the%20narrative%20of%20the%20conundrum%20of%20religiosity%20in%20India%20and%20its%20resolution.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20the%20Pran%20Prathistha%20of%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20event%20has%20been%20analyzed%20with%20perspicacity%20and%20insight%20in%20the%20critical%20media%3B%20here%20is%20my%20take%20on%20this%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20two%20contrary%20templates%20of%20the%20religiosity%20of%20Ayodhya.%20One%20of%20these%20is%20the%20conventional%20and%20orthodox.%20This%20is%20the%20version%20that%20validates%20the%20Shankaracharyas%E2%80%99%20insistence%20on%20being%20absent%20from%20the%20consecration.%20They%20justify%20this%20decision%20in%20terms%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20going%20ahead%20with%20the%20consecration%20in%20the%20tabooed%20state%20of%20the%20temple%20being%20incomplete%20and%20held%20on%20a%20date%20not%20particularly%20auspicious%20by%20the%20Hindu%20calendar.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20template%2C%20ironically%2C%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20orthodox%20version%3A%20it%20refers%20to%20the%20heterodoxy%20of%20Ram%20worship%20and%20its%20associated%20mythology%20and%20folklore.%20This%20is%20where%20the%20polyphony%20of%20the%20Ram%20tradition%2C%20the%20many%20versions%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20across%20time%20and%20space%2C%20the%20subaltern%20worship%20of%20Ram%2C%20and%20Ram%20as%20an%20exemplary%20human%20being%20%3Cem%3E(maryada%20purushottam%3C%2Fem%3E)%20rather%20than%20a%20deity%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20are%20forcefully%20adduced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%2C%20contemporaneously%2C%20contrary%20readings%20of%20the%20Ram-temple-complex%20if%20one%20may%20call%20it%20so.%20One%20of%20these%20alludes%20to%20desecration%20within%20the%20orthodox%20consecration.%20Here%2C%20I%20refer%20to%20those%20believers%20who%20resented%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20wanton%20destruction%20of%20old%20images%20and%20shrines%20to%20construct%20the%20modern%20Ganga%20Corridor%20in%20Varanasi%20ghats%2C%20for%20example.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20there%20are%20those%20protestors%20who%20are%20not%20yet%20reconciled%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20clearance%20for%20the%20building%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20while%20treating%20it%20as%20a%20land%20dispute%20rather%20than%20a%20heritage%20issue.%20Such%20is%20the%20view%20of%20a%20section%20of%20the%20modern%20Indian%20citizenry%20who%20are%20convinced%20that%20a%20raw%20deal%20was%20given%20%E2%80%93%20in%20terms%20of%20religiosity%20%E2%80%93%20to%20the%20Muslim%20minority%20in%20Ayodhya%20jurisdiction.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20also%2C%20to%20complicate%20the%20picture%20further%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98believer%E2%80%99%20Hindus%20who%20refer%20to%20the%20classical%20modes%20of%20Indian%20temple%20worship%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fram-mandir-consecration-will-it-get-sacred-status-for-hindus-or-remain-a-political-project-9114386%2F%5C%22%3Edistinguish%20between%20%E2%80%98monumental%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98organic%E2%80%99%20temples.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Arguably%2C%20the%20former%20are%20not%20principally%20the%20sites%20of%20worship%20by%20the%20devout%20Hindu%20masses%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20like%20touristic%20religious%20sites%20on%20the%20analogy%20of%20the%20Vatican%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20latter%20are%20hallowed%20sacred%20sites%20of%20worship%20mentioned%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Esthala%20puranas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20are%20holy%20sites%20(%3Cem%3Etirtha%3C%2Fem%3E)%20with%20scriptural%20sanction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20Three%20Signs%20of%20a%20New%20Cultural%20Defiance%20in%20India%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObviously%2C%20not%20unlike%20the%20autocratic%20Modi%20decision%20to%20impose%20sudden%20demonetisation%20on%20the%20Indian%20citizenry%2C%20this%20decision%20to%20consecrate%20the%20Ayodhya%20temple%20on%20January%2022%20is%20also%20seemingly%20obdurate%20and%20dictatorial.%20In%20effect%2C%20the%20decision%2C%20and%20its%20accompanying%20official%20fanfare%2C%20falls%20between%20the%20stools%20of%20orthodoxy%20and%20heterodoxy%2C%20stunning%20the%20Indian%20(or%20even%20Hindu)%20citizenry%20into%20an%20ennui%20of%20worship%2C%20faith%20and%20belief.%20One%20is%20not%20too%20sure%20if%20this%20ploy%20would%20delude%20the%20Hindu%20faithful%2C%20as%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP-RSS%20ardently%20wish%20and%20hope%20for%2C%20into%20voting%20for%20the%20Rightist%20party%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20general%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20and%20third%20events%20straddle%20between%20secularity%20and%20religiosity%20in%20a%20unique%20manner.%20The%20Republic%20Day%20extravaganza%20on%20January%2026%20cannot%20but%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98national%20temple%E2%80%99%20consecration%20where%20the%20republic%20was%20sought%20to%20be%C2%A0%20redefined%20through%20a%20kind%20of%20archaic%20divine%20kingship%20conflating%20kingship%20and%20priesthood.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20event%2C%20the%20anniversary%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20martyrdom%20on%20January%2030%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20reflection%20of%20a%20normative%20modern%20religiosity%20constituting%20the%20essence%20of%20Gandhian%20secularism%20in%20polar%20contrast%20to%20the%20archaism%20of%20Ram%20temple%20consecration.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%2C%20I%20base%20myself%20heavily%20on%20Saumya%20Malviya%E2%80%99s%20redaction%20of%20Gandhian%20secularism%20and%20martyrdom%20in%20relation%20to%20civil%20society%20as%20prompted%20by%20my%20sociological%20colleague%2C%20the%20late%20J.P.S.%20Uberoi.%20To%20paraphrase%20the%20argument%2C%20modern%20religiosity%2C%20whether%20ancillary%20to%20Sikhism%20or%20Jainism%2C%20builds%20itself%20on%20congregational%20esprit%20de%20corps%20in%20pursuit%20of%20an%20ideal%20marked%20by%20exemplary%20martyrdom.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERepresentation%20and%20vicariousness%20characterised%20this%20ethical%20leadership%20in%20sheer%20contrast%20to%20the%20archaic%20conflation%20of%20kingship%20and%20priesthood%20as%20in%20divine%20kingship.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20precisely%20is%20the%20intersectionality%20of%20religiosity%20that%20we%20call%20%E2%80%98modern%E2%80%99%20(in%20contrast%20to%20Hinduism%2C%20Islam%2C%20Christianity%20or%20Sikhism%20seen%20in%20isolation)%20on%20one%20hand%20and%20civil%20society%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20Indian%20civil%20society%20is%20essentially%20%E2%80%98religious%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20this%20sense%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Seen%20in%20this%20perspective%2C%20normatively%2C%20the%20Indian%20Republic%20of%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20dream%20(call%20it%20%3Cem%3ERam%20Rajya%3C%2Fem%3E%20if%20you%20like)%20is%20a%20palpable%20living%20reality%20and%20possibility.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20we%20have%20read%20the%20message%20and%20meaning%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20martyrdom%20correctly%20then%20we%20may%20say%20%E2%80%98the%20(old)%20Republic%20is%20dead%2C%20long%20live%20the%20(modern)%20Republic%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ERavindra%20K.%20Jain%20retired%20as%20Professor%20of%20Sociology%20at%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20New%20Delhi.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707052771000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F24162930%2FIMG_2541.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fthe-religiosity-conundrum-and-its-resolution%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20we%20have%20read%20the%20message%20and%20meaning%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20martyrdom%20correctly%20then%20we%20may%20say%