but%20found%20no%20signs%20of%20forced%20entry%20-%20the%20locks%20on%20the%20main%20door%20and%20the%20cupboard%20were%20found%20to%20be%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F681763c_stolen-jewellery-and-cash_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20then%20scoured%20through%20footage%20from%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20the%20area%20and%20spotted%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20burqa%20entering%20the%20home%20suspiciously.%20The%20police's%20technical%20investigation%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%2031-year-old%20Shweta%2C%20Kamlesh's%20elder%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%2C%20during%20questioning%2C%20revealed%20she%20planned%20this%20burglary%20because%20her%20mother%20loved%20her%20younger%20sister%20more%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20The%20feelings%20of%20jealousy%20and%20hatred%20overpowered%20her%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20also%20had%20some%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShweta%20told%20the%20police%20she%20hatched%20this%20elaborate%20plan%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20dues.%20Some%20of%20the%20jewellery%20she%20stole%20was%20hers%2C%20which%20she%20had%20asked%20her%20mother%20to%20keep%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20were%20made%20by%20her%20mother%20for%20her%20sister's%20wedding%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20revealed%20how%20she%20slowly%20built%20up%20to%20the%20day%20of%20the%20robbery%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Shweta%20first%20moved%20out%20of%20her%20mother's%20home%20in%20January%20to%20get%20the%20plan%20rolling.%20For%20a%20few%20days%2C%20Kamlesh%20helped%20her%20elder%20daughter%20arrange%20her%20new%20home.%20She%20would%20come%20to%20Shweta's%20place%20after%20her%20younger%20daughter%20left%20for%20work.%20Shweta%20took%20advantage%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20loot%2C%20Shweta%20first%20stole%20the%20keys%20to%20her%20mother's%20house%20and%20stepped%20out%20of%20her%20new%20home%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20buying%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20went%20into%20a%20public%20toilet%20to%20wear%20the%20burqa%20and%20reached%20her%20mother's%20house%2C%20where%20she%20opened%20the%20main%20door%20and%20cupboard%20locker%20with%20the%20keys%20and%20ran%20away%20with%20jewellery%20and%20cash.%20When%20Kamlesh%20found%20out%20about%20the%20robbery%20and%20informed%20her%2C%20Shweta%20pretended%20to%20be%20worried%20and%20upset%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20She%20thought%20no%20one%20would%20suspect%20her%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShweta%20reportedly%20told%20the%20cops%20that%20she%20had%20sold%20the%20jewellery.%20However%2C%20the%20police%20have%20managed%20to%20recover%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707051120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fot4usjkg_woman-robs-mothers-home_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-in-burqa-robs-own-home-because-mother-loved-sister-more-4992628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2031-year-old%20woman%20wore%20a%20burqa%2C%20broke%20into%20her%20mother's%20home%2C%20and%20stole%20jewellery%20and%20cash%2C%20worth%20lakhs%20in%20all%2C%20in%20Delhi's%20Uttam%20Nagar%20area%2C%20the%20police%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-in-burqa-robs-own-home-because-mother-loved-sister-more-4992628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-in-burqa-robs-own-home-because-mother-loved-sister-more-4992628%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwoman-in-burqa-robs-own-home-because-mother-loved-sister-more-4992628%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Space%20for%20Free%20Expression%20Shrinks%2C%20What%20Does%20the%20Future%20of%20Dissent%20Look%20Like%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01155958%2FDAEFC20B-9E9E-4268-B054-A64E9B81.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20yet%20another%20confirmation%20of%20how%20space%20for%20free%20expression%20is%20shrinking%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20a%20human%20rights%20conference%2C%20attended%20by%20some%20well-known%20names%20%E2%80%93%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate%20Prashant%20Bhushan%2C%20environmentalist%20Vandana%20Shiva%2C%20People%E2%80%99s%20Union%20for%20Civil%20Liberties%20leader%20Kavita%20Shrivastava%2C%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%20leader%20Medha%20Patkar%2C%20among%20others%20%E2%80%93%20was%20held%20at%20a%20private%20terrace%20in%20Ahmedabad%20instead%20of%20a%20public%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20seemed%20simple%2C%20and%20several%20speakers%20(ironically%2C%20not%20the%20organisers)%20stated%20it%20openly%3A%20It%E2%80%99s%20quite%20some%20time%20that%20no%20one%2C%20not%20even%20private%20hall%20owners%2C%20not%20to%20talk%20of%20state-supported%20halls%2C%20are%20available%20for%20those%20seeking%20to%20express%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi-founded%20Gujarat%20Vidyapeeth%20hall%20used%20to%20be%20available%20for%20such%20events%2C%20but%20following%20its%20%E2%80%9Ctakeover%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20governor%20in%202022-end%2C%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20available.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Mehdi%20Nawaz%20Jung%20Hall%20in%20Ahmedabad%20%3Cspan%3Ewas%20available%20%E2%80%93%20but%20since%20it%20is%20controlled%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20governor%2C%20it%20became%20a%20%E2%80%9Cno-no%E2%80%9D%20for%20rights%20leaders%20ever%20since%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20won%20the%20polls%20in%20May%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHeld%20under%20the%20auspices%20of%20a%20foundation%20named%20after%20perhaps%20the%20most%20well-known%20person%20among%20Gujarat%20advocates%20taking%20up%20human%20rights%20issues%2C%20late%20Girish%20Patel%2C%20the%20conference%20was%20attended%20mostly%20by%20like-minded%20persons%20%E2%80%93%20academics%2C%20lawyers%2C%20scholars%20and%20activists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOrganised%20by%20a%20team%20led%20by%20senior%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20advocate%20Anand%20Yagnik%2C%20a%20worthy%20Girish%20Patel%20disciple%2C%20the%20three%20day%20conference%20that%20began%20on%20January%2026%2C%20saw%20about%20150%20people%20each%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDiscussions%2C%20often%20focusing%20on%20specific%20areas%20like%20sugarcane%20workers%20of%20South%20Gujarat%20and%20salt%20pan%20workers%20of%20the%20Little%20Runn%20of%20Kutch%2C%20took%20place%20around%20human%20rights%20and%20their%20national%20and%20international%20perspectives%3B%20civil%20liberties%3B%20Adivasi%2C%20Dalit%2C%20farmer%2C%20minority%2C%20woman%20and%20child%20rights%3B%20environmental%20impact%20of%20infrastructure%20and%20development%20projects%3B%20environment%20and%20biodiversity%3B%20labour%20rights%20and%20minimum%20wages%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cins%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20read%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgn-devy-iit-bombay-cancelled-lecture%5C%22%3EThe%20Crisis%20Within%20Education%3A%20An%20Excerpt%20of%20G.N.%20Devy%E2%80%99s%20Lecture%20Which%20IIT-B%20Cancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20very%20few%20of%20its%20kind%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20conference%2C%20which%20ended%20on%20January%2028%2C%20saw%20participants%20confront%20the%20crucial%20question%3A%20Yes%2C%20we%20have%20discussed%20some%20of%20the%20most%20nagging%20issues%20concerning%20civil%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20especially%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20but%20what%20next%3F%20Where%20do%20we%20go%20from%20here%3F%20What%20do%20we%20do%20next%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMedha%20Patkar%2C%20who%20spoke%20at%20the%20concluding%20session%2C%20was%20frank%3A%20Admitting%20a%20huge%20gap%20between%20what%20the%20activists%20think%20and%20their%20desired%20action%2C%20she%20said%2C%20people%20still%20do%20not%20know%20what%20destruction%20the%20Rs%2090%2C000%20crore%20Narmada%20dam%20has%20brought%20about%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20the%20neighbouring%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20canals%20havn%E2%80%99t%20been%20built%20and%20waters%20haven%E2%80%99t%20reached%20the%20Kutch%20farmers%2C%20thousands%20of%20cusecs%20are%20being%20wasted%20away%20by%20releasing%20the%20waters%20in%20the%20Little%20Runn%20of%20Kutch%2C%20destroying%20the%20livelihood%20of%20saltpan%20workers%20operating%20there%2C%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatkar%20asked%20participants%20to%20visit%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20see%20for%20themselves%20how%20her%20organisation%2C%20Narmada%20Bachao%20Andolan%2C%20is%20leading%20protests%20against%20the%20huge%20tracts%20of%20land%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20villages%2C%20being%20submerged%20by%20Narmada%20waters%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20dam%2C%20considered%20by%20dominant%20sections%2C%20as%20lifeline%20of%20Gujarat.%20She%20later%20told%20%3Cem%3ECounterview%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20need%20to%20tell%20people%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20with%20Narmada%20waters%2C%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20being%20wasted.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20conference%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20train%20activists%2C%20making%20them%20aware%20of%20human%20rights%20issues%20and%20the%20legal%20tools%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20fight%20for%20the%20oppressed%20sections.%20All%20agreed%2C%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20hold%20similar%20conferences%2C%20a%20rarity%20now%2C%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%20in%20order%20to%20discuss%20and%20debate%20the%20issues%20confronting%20broader%20sections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20appeared%20to%20be%20no%20answer%20to%20how%20and%20where%20%E2%80%93%20except%20for%20the%20private%20terrace%20where%20the%20conference%20took%20place.%20Nor%20was%20anyone%20clear%20as%20to%20whether%20anything%20beyond%20training%20activists%20by%20turning%20them%20into%20para-legals%20%E2%80%93%20something%20that%20the%20Ahmedabad-based%20NGO%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Justice%20has%20been%20doing%20for%20decades%20now%2C%20in%20whatever%20limited%20way%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20read%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvindictive-witch-hunt-over-250-condemn-raids-on-harsh-mander%5C%22%3EVindictive%20Witch%20Hunt%E2%80%99%3A%20Over%20250%20Activists%2C%20Scholars%20Condemn%20Raids%20on%20Harsh%20Mander%20and%20His%20NGO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20senior%20journalist%2C%20who%20could%20not%20attend%20the%20conference%20because%20of%20personal%20reasons%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3ECounterview%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20have%20gone%20there%20only%20to%20keep%20my%20contacts%20alive%2C%20to%20meet%20them%E2%80%A6%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20fact%3A%20the%20participants%E2%80%99%20views%20are%20well-known%2C%20I%20presume%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20said%20anything%20new.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndeed%2C%20while%20there%20was%20a%20discussion%20at%20the%20conference%20on%20%E2%80%9Cviolence%20against%20women%20in%20social%20media%2F%20online%20violence%E2%80%9D%2C%20what%20seemed%20missing%20was%20ways%20to%20adopt%20the%20online%20tools%20which%20were%20not%20available%20to%20valiant%20but%20traditional%20agitators%20like%20Medha%20Patkar%20till%20now%20in%20order%20to%20discuss%20and%20propagate%20human%20and%20civil%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20issue%20is%20particularly%20significant%2C%20as%20there%20is%20an%20increasing%20view%20among%20civil%20society%20groups%20that%20the%20established%20media%20%E2%80%93%20print%20or%20electronic%20%E2%80%93%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20responsive%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20needs%20and%20aspirations%20of%20the%20civil%20society.%20And%20how%20could%20it%20be%3F%20Their%20owners%20and%20their%20supporting%20journalists%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2014%2F09%2Fwe-want-to-annihilate-caste-but-without.html%5C%22%3Ethink%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20news%20is%20nothing%20but%20family%20business.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFew%20in%20the%20civil%20society%20seem%20to%20understand%20that%20times%20have%20changed%20%E2%80%93%20a%20factor%20predicted%2C%20ironically%2C%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Mohammad%20Yunus%2C%20the%20Grameen%20Bank%20man%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20in%20his%20book%20titled%3Cem%3E%20Bankers%20to%20the%20Poor%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20first%20published%20way%20back%20in%201998%2C%20when%20information%20and%20communication%20technology%20(ICT)%20was%20in%20its%20nascent%20stage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHounded%20by%20Bangladesh%20authorities%20today%2C%20Yunus%2C%20now%2083%2C%20had%20said%20then%2C%20ICT%20was%20going%20to%20%E2%80%9Cchange%20the%20world%20in%20the%20immediate%20future%20far%20more%20rapidly%20and%20fundamentally%20than%20any%20other%20technology%20so%20far%20in%20human%20history.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20chapter%20%E2%80%98Poverty%20Free%20World%3A%20How%20and%20When%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20top%20economist%E2%80%99s%20words%20were%20prophetic%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20attractive%20aspect%20of%20this%20spread%20of%20ICT%20is%20that%20it%20is%20not%20in%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20control.%20Neither%20government%2C%20nor%20big%20business%2C%20nor%20anyone%20of%20any%20authority%20can%20restrict%20the%20flow%20of%20information.%20The%20next%20best%20aspect%20of%20it%20is%20that%20it%20is%20becoming%20cheaper%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYunus%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CICT%20is%20raising%20the%20hope%20that%20we%20are%20approaching%20the%20world%20which%20is%20free%20from%20power%20brokers%2C%20and%20knowledge%20brokers%E2%80%9D%2C%20pointing%20out%2C%20the%20ICT%20revolution%20was%20going%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cparticularly%20exciting%20for%20all%20disadvantaged%20groups%2C%20voiceless%20groups%2C%20and%20minority%20groups.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20insisted%2C%20%E2%80%9CAny%20power%20based%20on%20exclusive%20access%20to%20information%20will%20disintegrate.%20Any%20common%20citizen%20will%20have%20almost%20as%20much%20access%20to%20information%20as%20the%20head%20of%20government.%20Leadership%20will%20have%20to%20be%20based%20on%20vision%20and%20integrity%2C%20rather%20than%20on%20manipulation%20of%20information%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFew%20appear%20to%20understand%20that%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20despite%20the%20big%20business%20efforts%20to%20control%20social%20media%20media%20and%20news.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20not%20be%20fashionable%20to%20quote%20Karl%20Marx%20today%2C%20as%20it%20was%20in%201970s.%20But%20what%20Yunus%20said%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20views%20enunciated%20way%20back%20in%201859%20in%20%3Cem%3EContribution%20to%20the%20Critique%20of%20Political%20Economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CNo%20social%20order%20is%20ever%20destroyed%20before%20all%20the%20productive%20forces%20for%20which%20it%20is%20sufficient%20have%20been%20developed%2C%20and%20new%20superior%20relations%20of%20production%20never%20replace%20older%20ones%20before%20the%20material%20conditions%20for%20their%20existence%20have%20matured%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20the%20old%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20established%20Communists%20have%20may%20not%20have%20paid%20heed%20to%20this%20truth%2C%20Yunus%E2%80%99%20views%20on%20ICT%20suggest%20the%20correctness%20of%20Marx%E2%80%99s%20views.%C2%A0One%20wonders%3A%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20it%20time%20civil%20society%20heeds%20the%20voice%20of%20reason%20of%20Yunus%20and%20Marx%20and%20consider%20ICT%20as%20a%20means%20to%20change%20amidst%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2024%2F01%2Fbroadcasting-bill-to-control-digital.html%5C%22%3Elatest%20move%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20regularise%20online%20media%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F2024%2F01%2Fas-free-space-shrinks-gujarat-human.html%3Futm_source%3Dsubstack%26utm_medium%3Demail%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.counterview.net%2F%5C%22%3ECounterview%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20style.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707049838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01155958%2FDAEFC20B-9E9E-4268-B054-A64E9B81.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-space-for-free-expression-shrinks-what-does-the-future-of-dissent-look-like%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Organisers%20of%20a%20human%20rights%20meet%20in%20Gujarat%20said%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20quite%20some%20time%20since%20no%20one%2C%20not%20even%20private%20hall%20owners%2C%20not%20to%20talk%20of%20state-supported%20halls%2C%20are%20available%20for%20those%20seeking%20to%20express%20dissent.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-space-for-free-expression-shrinks-what-does-the-future-of-dissent-look-like%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samsung%20is%20removing%20thi