n%20India%20Based%20Security%20Assistant%20(IBSA)%20at%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20since%202021%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MEA%E2%80%99s%20bureau%20of%20security%20enlists%20India-Based%20Security%20Assistants%20from%20constables%20and%20head%20constables%20within%20state%20police%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpolice.py.gov.in%2FDeputation%2520Call%2520for%2520PC%2520and%2520HC%2520-%2520Bureau%2520of%2520Security%2C%2520MEA%2520dt.03.09.18.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%202018%20notification%20inviting%20applications%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20IBSAs%20are%20chosen%20for%20deputation%20for%20three%20years%2C%20with%20a%20mandatory%20minimum%20of%20two%20years%20to%20be%20spent%20posted%20at%20a%20diplomatic%20mission%20abroad.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20departing%20for%20their%20international%20assignments%2C%20candidates%20undergo%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20familiarise%20themselves%20with%20the%20security-oriented%20structure%20of%20a%20diplomatic%20facility.%20This%20training%20also%20encompasses%20the%20maintenance%20of%20security%20devices%20responsible%20for%20controlling%20access%2C%20scanning%20personnel%20and%20vehicles%2C%20and%20ensuring%20the%20overall%20security%20of%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20training%20underlines%2C%20the%20job%20profile%20of%20a%20Security%20Assistant%20revolves%20around%20safeguarding%20both%20the%20premises%20and%20personnel%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20mission.%20Additional%20responsibilities%20may%20be%20assigned%20based%20on%20the%20specific%20requirements%20of%20the%20embassy.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202017%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fisi-bid-to-honeytrap-3-indian-officials-in-islamabad-foiled%2Farticleshow%2F62100692.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20reca