20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20challenging%20the%20ED%20arrest%20but%20when%20he%20filed%20a%20similar%20petition%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Sibal%20undertook%20that%20he%20would%20withdraw%20the%20high%20court%20petition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20Article%2032%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20which%20states%20that%20individuals%20have%20the%20right%20to%20approach%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20enforcement%20of%20other%20fundamental%20rights%20recognised%20by%20the%20constitution%2C%20Sibal%20said%20that%20the%20apex%20court%20must%20make%20a%20policy%20under%20which%20the%20public%20should%20know%20when%20to%20approach%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20there%20would%20hardly%20have%20been%20any%20such%20instance%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India%20when%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20is%20arrested%20and%20that%20is%20also%20not%20deserving%20to%20be%20heard%20under%20Article%2032.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20heard%20us%20and%20then%2C%20after%20hearing%20it%2C%20said%20%E2%80%98we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20interfere%20and%20go%20to%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99.%20But%20to%20tell%20us%20first%20that%20we%20should%20go%20to%20high%20court%20without%20hearing%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Union%20government%2C%20Sibal%20said%20that%20the%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20opposition%20chief%20minister%20in%20any%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20do%20this%20against%20%5BDelhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%5D%20Kejriwal.%20They%20want%20only%20double-engine%20governments%20and%20no%20opposition%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20what%20will%20happen%20is%20that%2010%20more%20cases%20will%20be%20slapped%20on%20Hemant%20Soren%20while%20in%20custody.%20All%20of%20them%20made-up%20cases%2C%20so%20that%20he%20does%20not%20come%20out%20of%20jail%20and%20which%20will%20benefit%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArrested%20in%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20Soren%20stepped%20down%20as%20chief%20minister%20late%20on%20January%2031.%20While%20leaders%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Janmukti%20Morcha%2C%20have%20noted%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%20%E2%80%93%20just%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20and%20called%20it%20a%20brazen%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta%2C%20Soren%20had%20expressed%20fear%20that%20his%20arrest%20may%20allow%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20also%20invoked%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20against%20ED%20officers%20for%20allegedly%20harassing%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESibal%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20relates%20to%202007%2C%20but%20the%20arrest%20took%20place%20in%202024.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20where%20will%20we%20go%3F%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20country%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20politics%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707044413000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02115438%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-must-make-policy-on-when-it-can-be-approached-sibal-on-hemant-sorens-plea%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20February%202%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20Soren%20through%20his%20counsel%20to%20approach%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-must-make-policy-on-when-it-can-be-approached-sibal-on-hemant-sorens-plea%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Crisis%20Within%20Education%3A%20An%20Excerpt%20of%20G.N.%20Devy's%20Lecture%20Which%20IIT-B%20Cancelled%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21135412%2FIMG_2345.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELast%20week%2C%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Bombay%2C%20cancelled%20a%20lecture%20by%20celebrated%20scholar%20G.N.%20Devy.%20Reports%20said%20that%20the%20committee%20to%20regulate%20such%20lectures%20decided%20to%20call%20it%20off%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20its%20delivery%20on%20January%2031.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20present%20century%20is%20often%20described%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20century%E2%80%99.%20We%20cannot%20be%20sure%20if%20this%20tag%20will%20stay%20valid%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century%20or%20whether%20future%20historians%20will%20characterise%20this%20period%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Age%20of%20Knowledge%E2%80%99%20as%20has%20been%20the%20case%20with%20the%20Dark%20Ages%20or%20the%20Age%20of%20Reason%20in%20the%20past.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20the%20description%20sums%20up%20the%20euphoria%20resulting%20from%20the%20information%20explosion%20and%20the%20technologies%20surrounding%20the%20exponential%20growth%20in%20the%20information%20generated%20every%20passing%20second.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20this%20epithet%20may%20not%20be%20sufficiently%20adequate%20for%20characterizing%20our%20time.%20The%20century%20has%20also%20been%20forecast%20to%20be%20the%20era%20of%20water%20wars%2C%20an%20age%20of%20deathless%20humans%2C%20an%20epoch%20of%20ecological%20termination%2C%20and%20the%20moment%20for%20an%20irreversible%20merger%20of%20the%20physical%20and%20the%20digital.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20century%E2%80%99%20label%20is%20open%20to%20discussion%20and%20is%20not%20incontestable.%20Indeed%2C%20self-perceptions%20of%20human%20civilizations%20can%20change%20quite%20radically%20over%20a%20relatively%20short%20temporal%20span.%20But%20if%20at%20all%2C%20the%20present%20century%20can%20be%20viewed%20as%20a%20unique%20era%20in%20human%20history%2C%20marking%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20engagement%20with%20what%20is%20considered%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%2C%20it%20would%20be%20interesting%20to%20reflect%20on%20where%20India%20stands%20in%20relation%20to%20this%20new%20turn%20in%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20with%20any%20certainty%20for%20want%20of%20the%C2%A0%20census%20that%20was%20to%20take%20place%20in%202021%2C%20perhaps%20India%20has%20already%C2%A0%20surpassed%20China%E2%80%99s%20population%20level.%20Also%2C%20the%20demographic%20proportion%20of%20the%20younger%20population%20in%20India%20at%20present%20is%20the%20largest%20ever%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20with%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20population%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025.%20Of%20the%20entire%20global%20population%2C%20nearly%20one%20in%20every%2012%20humans%20is%20a%20young%20Indian%20for%20whom%20meaningful%20education%20is%20the%20most%20assured%20means%20of%20finding%20a%20decent%20livelihood.%20Education%2C%20knowledge%20production%20and%20research%20leading%20to%20widening%20of%20the%20horizons%20of%20thought%20and%20imagination%2C%20therefore%2C%20ought%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20important%20concerns%20of%20our%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EConsiderations%20of%20how%20and%20how%20much%20knowledge%20is%20produced%2C%20how%20it%20is%20transacted%20and%20how%20it%20is%20responding%20to%20social%20inequalities%20and%20ecological%20disconnect%20add%20to%20the%20vastness%20and%20complexities%20involved%20in%20a%20study%20of%20knowledge%20and%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaving%20spent%20close%20to%20half%20a%20century%20in%20and%20around%20universities%2C%20and%20having%20elsewhere%20presented%20academic%20research%20and%20essays%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20not%20too%20inappropriate%20to%20present%20my%20observations%20on%20the%20theme%20through%20a%20reflective%20statement.%20I%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20present%20a%20position%20or%20positions%20in%20it.%20Quite%20often%2C%20analytical%20studies%20have%20a%20purely%20subjective%20weave%20as%20their%20flip%20side%2C%20a%20tacit%20class-bias%20presented%20as%20%E2%80%98objective%E2%80%99%20culture-critique.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20the%20extent%20possible%2C%20I%20have%20avoided%20such%20analysis.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20would%20therefore%20like%20to%20describe%20this%20lecture%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98reflections%E2%80%99%20of%20a%20person%20for%20whom%20knowledge%20and%20education%20have%20been%20serious%20concerns%20for%20several%20decades.%20When%20I%20began%20working%20as%20a%20young%20researcher%20in%20literary%20studies%20in%20the%20early%20post-Independence%20years%2C%20the%20colonial%20experience%20was%20the%20obsessive%20interest%20of%20the%20day.%20Most%20forms%20of%20formal%20knowledge%2C%20scientific%20disciplines%20and%20social%20sciences%20were%20seen%20as%20having%20originated%20in%20the%20colonial%20%E2%80%98transfer%20of%20knowledge%E2%80%99.%20Scholarly%20debates%20revolved%20around%20the%20question%20of%20acceptance%20or%20rejection%20of%20these%20forms%20of%20knowledge.%20These%20debates%20were%20happening%20in%20several%20disciplines%2C%20if%20not%20all%20of%20them%2C%20ranging%20from%20history%20to%20literature%2C%20architecture%20to%20aesthetics%3B%20but%20invariably%20the%20reference%20point%20was%20the%20knowledge%20of%20the%20colonial%20mind.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20interest%20started%20shifting%20to%20discussion%20of%20disparities%20inherent%20in%20every%20intellectual%20transaction%20between%20the%20colonizing%20Western%20cultures%20and%20the%20post-colonial%20societies.%20These%20discussions%20were%20fascinating%20and%20produced%20several%20works%20of%20great%20brilliance.%20They%20gained%20in%20significance%20as%20similar%20discussions%20had%20been%20taking%20place%20in%20other%20post-colonial%20cultures.%20In%20Western%20intellectual%20circles%20too%20colonialism%20and%20post-colonialism%20acquired%20as%20much%20centrality%20as%20the%20Cold%20War%20and%20imperialism%20had%20enjoyed%20earlier.%20I%20have%20chosen%20to%20overlook%20in%20this%20address%20many%20of%20the%20valuable%20insights%20generated%20over%20the%20decades%20in%20both%20these%20phases%20as%20they%20are%20by%20now%20well-settled%20in%20the%20arena%20of%20the%20history%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20cultural%20relations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fslack-imgs-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%20many%20different%20ways%20to%20approach%20the%20thorny%20issue%20of%20decolonising%20knowledge.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221356%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-143400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20have%20witnessed%20rapidly%20sinking%20fortunes%20of%20%E2%80%98natural%20memory%E2%80%99%2C%20technology%20of%20knowledge%20incubation%20and%20knowledge%20reception%2C%20and%20the%20sanitisation%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20effected%20through%20several%20exclusions.%20Photo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%2C%20however%2C%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20enormous%20amount%20of%20descriptive%20and%20analytical%20studies%20that%20those%20two%20moves%20produced%2C%20both%20within%20India%20and%20outside%2C%20I%20begin%20by%20briefly%20alluding%20to%20some%20of%20the%20iconic%20period-statements%20in%20the%20next%20section%2C%20before%20moving%20to%20the%20discussion%20of%20the%20more%20contemporary%2C%20and%20no%20less%20significant%20phenomena%20having%20a%20profound%20bearing%20on%20the%20question%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20and%20education%20in%20India.%20These%20phenomena%20include%20the%20rapidly%20sinking%20fortunes%20of%20%E2%80%98natural%20memory%E2%80%99%2C%20technology%20of%20knowledge%20incubation%20and%20knowledge%20reception%2C%20and%20the%20sanitisation%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20effected%20through%20several%20exclusions%20%E2%80%93%20linguistic%2C%20ethnic%20and%20epistemic.%20This%20book%2C%20therefore%2C%20reflects%20on%20the%20condition%20and%20crisis%20of%20knowledge%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%2C%20by%20implication%2C%20about%20the%20condition%20and%20crisis%20of%20our%20democracy.%20In%20order%20to%20analyse%20the%20present%20status%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20and%20the%20problems%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20higher%20education%2C%20this%20lecture%20will%20focus%20on%20four%20important%20elements%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20Indian%20tradition(s)%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20trajectory%20of%20%E2%80%98memory%E2%80%99%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20patterns%20of%20social%20exclusion%20and%20their%20effect%20on%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20construction%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20%3Cstrong%3Efinally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20technology%20on%20the%20forms%20of%20knowledge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20ancient%20civilisation%2C%20with%20amazing%20wealth%20of%20philosophical%2C%20literary%20and%20scientific%20treatises%20and%20unparalleled%20continuity%20of%20%E2%80%98the%20life%20of%20the%20mind%E2%80%99%2C%20India%20nonetheless%20was%20not%20at%20its%20most%20creative%20when%20the%20colonial%20scholars%20started%20exploring%20Indian%20thought%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018th%20century.%20Besides%2C%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20complicated%20reasons%2C%20the%20creative%20springs%20of%20ideas%20and%20imagination%20current%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebhashas%3C%2Fem%3E%20at%20that%20time%20were%20not%20found%20to%20be%20of%20sufficient%20interest%20by%20the%20colonial%20English%20officers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20focus%20remained%20almost%20entirely%20on%20literature%20and%20the%20texts%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20Persian.%20Given%20the%20context%20of%20political%20domination%2C%20even%20a%20rather%20casual%20compliment%20from%20Goethe%20for%20the%20imaginative%20power%20of%20Kalidasa%E2%80%99s%20play%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EShakuntalam%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eappeared%20to%20the%20Indian%20mind%20as%20great%20a%20victory%20as%2C%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20Nobel%20Prize%20in%20Literature%20for%20Rabindranath%20Tagore.%20During%20that%20one%20and%20a%20quarter%20century%20%E2%80%93%20from%20the%20founding%20of%20the%20Asiatic%20Society%20in%20the%201780s%20to%20the%20beginning%20of%20World%20War%20I%20and%20the%20struggle%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20%E2%80%93%20any%20compliment%20from%20a%20European%20scholar%20was%20generally%20hugely%20overvalued%2C%20reflecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20complete%20loss%20of%20cultural%20self-confidence.%20Hence%2C%20the%20generous%20praise%20that%20Friedrich%20Max%20M%C3%BCller%20lavished%20on%20Indian%20thought%20was%20received%20by%20the%20Brahminical%20classes%20with%20ecstasy.%20He%20stated%20in%20a%20lecture%20to%20the%20Indian%20Civil%20Service%20aspirants%20in%20London%3A%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20were%20asked%20under%20what%20sky%20the%20human%20mind%20has%20most%20fully%20developed%20some%20of%20its%20choicest%20gifts%2C%20has%20most%20deeply%20pondered%20over%20the%20greatest%20problems%20of%20life%2C%20and%20has%20found%20solutions%20of%20some%20of%20them%20which%20well%20deserve%20the%20attention%20even%20of%20those%20who%20have%20studied%20Plato%20and%20Kant%2C%20I%20should%20point%20to%20India.%20And%20if%20I%20were%20to%20ask%20myself%20from%20what%20literature%20we%20who%20have%20been%20nurtured%20almost%20exclusively%20on%20the%20thoughts%20of%20Greeks%20and%20Romans%2C%20and%20of%20the%20Semitic%C2%A0%20race%2C%20the%20Jewish%2C%20may%20draw%20the%20corrective%20which%20is%20most%20wanted%20in%20order%20to%20make%20our%20inner%20life%20more%20established%20after%20the%20European%20pattern%20were%20too%20expensive%20for%20the%20people%2C%20and%20therefore%20they%20could%20not%20possibly%20overtake%20the%20thing.%20I%20defy%20anybody%20to%20fulfil%20a%20programme%20of%20compulsory%20primary%20education%20of%20these%20masses%20inside%20of%20a%20century.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20century%20after%20the%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20uncharacteristically%20passionate%20outburst%2C%20if%20we%20are%20to%20take%20a%20relatively%20more%20objective%20view%20of%20the%20colonial%20impact%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20knowledge%20traditions%2C%20two%20significant%20elements%20deserve%20attention.%20The%20first%20of%20these%20is%20that%20the%20pervasive%20cultural%20amnesia%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20failures%20and%20accomplishments%20seems%20to%20have%20hampered%20our%20ability%20to%20establish%20organic%20links%20between%20the%20past%20and%20the%20present.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%2C%20Indians%20have%20either%20entirely%20dismissed%20all%20that%20we%20had%20cultivated%20as%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20theory%20as%20well%20as%20a%20million%20everyday%20tasks.%20Or%20else%2C%20we%20tend%20to%20think%20that%20ancient%20India%20had%20all-encompassing%20knowledge%20in%20all%20domains%20and%20tend%20to%20glorify%20that%20imagined%20past.%20But%20unquestioning%20adulation%20or%20complete%20dismissal%20is%20no%20substitute%20for%20a%20critical%20perspective.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20lecture%20hall%20at%20IIT-Kharagpur.%20Credit%3A%20ambuj%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F421073631_1459759ec3_b-300x225.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-8858%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98T%3Cspan%3Ehe%20intensity%20with%20which%20Indian%20scholars%20have%20felt%20this%20discriminating%20attitude%20has%20been%20acute.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Photo%3A%20ambuj%2FFlickr%2C%20CC%20BY%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20element%20was%20the%20frequently%20noticed%20%E2%80%98time%20lag%E2%80%99%20between%20the%20knowledge%20in%20the%20West%20and%20that%20in%20India%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20parity%20between%20knowledge%20production%20in%20the%20global%20West%20and%20the%20global%20South.%20Countries%20such%20as%20Ireland%2C%20Canada%20and%20Australia%20too%20had%20to%20fight%20Western%20disapproval%20of%20knowledge%20coming%20from%20former%20colonies.%20But%20the%20intensity%20with%20which%20Indian%20scholars%20have%20felt%20this%20discriminating%20attitude%20has%20generally%20been%20more%20acute.%20It%20would%20be%20fair%20to%20add%20that%20the%20colonised%20African%20countries%20have%20had%20an%20even%20greater%20difficulty%20in%20having%20their%20forms%20of%20knowledge%20acknowledged%20as%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20knowledge.%20The%20African%20reactions%20too%20have%20been%20far%20more%20pointed.%20As%20a%20result%20a%20whole%20cultural%20movement%20called%20%E2%80%98Negritude%E2%80%99%20sprang%20up%20in%20reaction%20in%20many%20African%20countries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENgugi%20Wa%20Thiong%E2%80%99o%2C%20the%20most%20eloquent%20of%20the%20spokespersons%20for%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20selfhood%2C%20wrote%20in%20his%20memorable%20book%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMoving%20the%20Centre%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Struggle%20for%20Cultural%20Freedoms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20suspicious%20of%20the%20uses%20of%20the%20word%20(the%20Third%20World)%20and%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20universal.%20For%20very%20often%2C%20this%20has%20meant%20the%20West%20generalising%20its%20experience%20of%20history%20as%20the%20universal%20experience%20of%20the%20world.%20What%20is%20Western%20becomes%20universal%20and%20what%20is%20Third%20World%20becomes%20local%E2%80%A6%20The%20Eurocentric%20basis%20of%20seeing%20the%20world%20has%20often%20meant%20marginalising%20into%20the%20periphery%20that%20which%20comes%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20colonial%20disruption%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20self-perception%20and%20the%20uneven%20cultural%20relationship%20emerging%20out%20of%20the%20context%20of%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20intellectual%20domination%20of%20the%20colonised%20people%20continued%20to%20prevail%20well%20beyond%20the%20formal%20end%20of%20colonial%20rule.%20The%20intellectual%20biography%20of%20D.%20D.%20Kosambi%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20more%20original%20thinkers%20in%20the%20post-Independence%20decades%2C%20brings%20home%20poignantly%20the%20cultural%20asymmetry%20in%20the%20field%20of%20%E2%80%98universal%E2%80%99%20sciences.%20Reflecting%20on%20the%20response%20to%20his%20fundamental%20contribution%20to%20number%20theory%20in%20mathematics%2C%20Kosambi%20observes%20that%20an%20Indian%20contribution%20to%20a%20theoretical%20field%20of%20knowledge%20usually%20met%20with%20suspicion%20and%20disregard.%20When%20Kosambi%20proposed%20that%20the%20Poisson%20distribution%20would%20explain%20the%20prime%20number%20theory%2C%20he%20had%20to%20spend%20several%20years%20to%20get%20a%20sympathetic%20audience%20among%20Western%20mathematicians.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20comments%20in%20despair%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20competent%20judge%20who%20saw%20only%20this%20radically%20new%20basic%20result%20intuitively%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20correct%20as%20well%20as%20of%20fundamental%20importance.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Riemann%20hypothesis%20followed%20as%20a%20simple%20consequence.%20Could%20a%20problem%20over%20which%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20greatest%20mathematicians%20have%20come%20to%20grief%20for%20over%20a%20century%20thus%20casually%20be%20solved%20in%20the%20jungles%20of%20India%3F%20Psychologically%2C%20it%20seemed%20much%20more%20probable%20that%20the%20interloper%20was%20just%20another%20%E2%80%98circle-squarer%E2%80%99.%20Mathematics%20may%20be%20a%20cold%2C%20impersonal%20science%20of%20pure%20thought%3B%20the%20mathematician%20can%20be%20thoughtless%2C%20heatedly%20acrid%2C%20even%20rabid%2C%20over%20what%20he%20dislikes%E2%80%A6%20I%20had%20to%20fight%20for%20my%20results%20over%20three%20long%20years%E2%80%A6%20There%20is%20surely%20a%20great%20deal%20to%20be%20said%20for%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20success%20of%20science%20is%20fundamentally%20related%20to%20the%20particular%20form%20of%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20my%20own%20work%2C%20during%20my%20formative%20years%2C%20I%20have%20often%20taken%20a%20position%20that%20would%20be%20akin%20to%20Dharampal%E2%80%99s%20painstaking%20research%2C%20showing%20how%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%20India%20destroyed%20the%20traditions%20of%20education%20existing%20during%20the%20immediately%20preceding%20era.%20I%20have%20also%20commented%20in%20detail%20on%20the%20cultural%20amnesia%20that%20set%20in%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20colonial%20encounter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20several%20eminent%20thinkers%20and%20educationists%20and%20various%20reports%20on%20education%20have%20pointed%20out%20the%20loss%20of%20originality%20in%20pedagogic%20practices%20and%20knowledge%20production%20in%20India%20caused%20by%20the%20imposition%20of%20a%20language%20that%20is%20not%20one%E2%80%99s%20mother%20tongue%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20higher%20order%20cognitive%20transactions.%20However%2C%20though%20the%20colonial%20experience%20can%20be%20justifiably%20held%20responsible%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20disproportionately%20low%20contribution%20to%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%2C%20focusing%20on%20colonialism%20alone%20may%20not%20yield%20the%20complete%20story%20of%20our%20failure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20possible%20to%20counterpoise%20Dharampal%E2%80%99s%20research%20with%20another%20significant%20work%20of%20research%2C%20one%20that%20has%20had%20equally%20enormous%20impact%2C%20but%20quite%20differently%2C%20on%20our%20self%20perception.%20That%20work%20is%20the%20text%20of%20a%20lecture%20that%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%20was%20to%20deliver%20at%20Lahore%20%E2%80%93%20but%20could%20not%20%E2%80%93%20and%20was%20published%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20book%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAnnihilation%20of%20Caste%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%201936.%20Ambedkar%20presents%20in%20this%20work%20a%20scathing%20analysis%20of%20the%20social%20inequalities%20prevailing%20in%20India%20for%20over%20two%20millennia%20and%20a%20passionate%20plea%20for%20genuine%20equality.%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20educated%20of%20the%20Indian%20leaders%20of%20his%20time%20with%20degrees%20from%20Columbia%20University%20and%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22school%20education%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F19090359%2FIMG_1911-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98To%20educate%E2%80%99%20the%20deprived%20classes%20to%20create%20an%20equitable%20society%20was%20one%20of%20his%20non-negotiable%20articles%20of%20faith.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20opens%20up%20the%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20question%20in%20India%2C%20taking%20it%20beyond%20the%20easily%20available%20proof%20of%20the%20culpability%20of%20colonial%C2%A0%20domination%2C%20and%20takes%20it%20back%20to%20the%20ancient%20times%20when%20various%20theological%20schools%20inscribed%20discrimination%20as%20a%20social%20norm%20in%20India.%20My%20purpose%20is%C2%A0%20not%20to%20judge%20Gandhi%20or%20Ambedkar.%20It%20is%20common%20among%20Indian%20intellectuals%20to%20position%20Gandhi%20and%20Ambedkar%20as%20intellectual%20adversaries%20and%20take%20umbrage%20on%20behalf%20of%20one%20or%20the%20other.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20aim%20is%20not%20to%20assess%20either%20Ambedkar%20or%20Gandhi%20and%20their%20views%20on%20knowledge%20or%20education%3B%20the%20aim%20here%20is%20to%20look%20at%20the%20question%20of%20knowledge%20and%20its%20formally%20institutionalised%20means%2C%20education.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20the%20past%20and%20in%20the%20present%2C%20the%20colonial%20cultural%20domination%20and%20the%20continued%20%E2%80%98knowledge%20imperialism%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20West%2C%20have%20had%20an%20effect%20in%20reducing%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20pauperisation%20and%20%E2%80%98education%E2%80%99%20in%20India%20to%20a%20savage%20mockery%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20education.%20To%20take%20both%20these%20givens%20into%20account%20should%20benefit%20any%20analysis%20of%20the%C2%A0%20condition%20of%20education%20in%20contemporary%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%2C%20as%20the%20650%20million%20Indians%20born%20after%201990%20look%20up%20to%20moving%20forward%20into%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20with%20education%20as%20their%20most%20desired%20means%20for%20that%20movement%20and%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20driving%20engine%20for%20their%20very%20survival%2C%20it%20may%20be%20beneficial%20if%20an%20analysis%20of%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20carried%20out%20from%20%E2%80%98within%E2%80%99%2C%20by%20looking%20at%20itself%20without%20unduly%20shifting%20the%20focus%20to%20the%20impact%20of%20colonialism%20or%20the%20legacy%20of%20caste%20hegemony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20I%20do%20not%20intend%20in%20the%20least%20to%20deny%20the%20primacy%20of%20these%20factors%20in%20any%20analysis%20of%20the%20condition%20of%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EG.N.%20Devy%20is%20a%20former%20professor%20and%20cultural%20activist%2C%20best%20known%20for%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Linguistic%20Survey%20of%20India%3Cem%3E%20and%20the%20Adivasi%20Academy%20created%20by%20him.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707043824000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F21135412%2FIMG_2345.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgn-devy-iit-bombay-cancelled-lecture%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Though%20the%20colonial%20experience%20can%20be%20justifiably%20held%20responsible%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20disproportionately%20low%20contribution%20to%20%E2%80%98knowledge%E2%80%99%20during%20the%20last%20two%20centuries%2C%20focusing%20on%20colonialism%20alone%20may%20not%20yield%20the%20complete%20story%20of%20our%20failure.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fgn-devy-iit-bombay-cancelled-lecture%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Existing%20taxation%20structure%20for%20corporates%20very%20reasonable%3A%20Revenue%20secy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707042860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-01%2F14%2Ffull%2F1610565102-1988.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Companies%20opting%20for%20these%20new%20tax%20rates%20had%20to%20forego%20all%20exemptions%20and%20incentives.%20The%20effective%20tax%20rate%20for%20existing%20units%2C%20after%20considering%20surcharges%20and%20cess%20--%20such%20as%20Swachh%20Bharat%20cess%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fexisting-taxation-structure-for-corporates-very-reasonable-revenue-secy-124020400329_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Past%2C%20Present%20and%20Future%20of%20Resistance%20in%20Myanmar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F10235624%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_05.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20civil%20war%20in%20Myanmar%20entered%20its%20fourth%20year%20on%20February%201%20and%20has%20been%20fanning%20unrest%20and%20insurgency%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20northeast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20decision%20last%20month%20to%20fence%20the%20entire%201%2C643-km%20border%20with%20Myanmar%20and%20suspend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffencing-border-with-myanmar-ending-free-movement-regime-soon-amit-shah%5C%22%3EFree%20Movement%20Regime%3C%2Fa%3E%20(FMR)%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20both%20chief%20ministers%20of%20Nagaland%20and%20Mizoram%20as%20these%20measures%20will%20divide%20their%20kith%20and%20kin%20across%20the%20border.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20fighting%20between%20the%20junta%20and%20resistance%20forces%20spilled%20over%20to%20north%20east%20from%20Rakhine%20and%20Arakan%20states%20in%20Myanmar%20and%20nearly%20800%20junta%20soldiers%20who%20had%20taken%20refuge%20on%20the%20Indian%20side%20were%20flown%20back.%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20insurgent%20groups%20sheltering%20in%20border%20regions%20of%20Myanmar%20have%20exploited%20the%20intense%20violence%20(since%20early%20May%20last%20year)%20that%20has%20been%20fuelled%20by%20the%20loss%20of%206%2C000%20weapons%20from%20Manipur%20state%20armouries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20has%20been%20grossly%20mismanaged%20by%20state%20and%20central%20authorities%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20once%20dormant%20eastern%20border%20has%20become%20live%20and%20vulnerable%20due%20to%20the%20junta%20losing%20operational%20control%20to%20resistance%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20coup%20in%20February%202021%20is%20the%20sixth%20successful%20coup%20since%201962%20by%20Myanmarese%20military%2C%20also%20called%20Tatmadaw%20or%20Sit%20Tat.%20Junta%20forces%20have%20inflicted%20coups%20more%20times%20than%20any%20other%20military%20in%20the%20world%20with%20profound%20expertise.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20national%20resistance%20has%20been%20cobbled%20to%20try%20to%20unhinge%20the%20military%20rule%20though%20the%20opposition%20has%20not%20thought%20about%20the%20end%20game.%20Resistance%20forces%20consist%20of%20Ethnic%20Armed%20Organisations%20(EAOs)%2C%20local%20militias%2C%20and%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Defence%20Force%20(PDF)%2C%20a%20majority%20Burman%20ethnic%20group%20created%20by%20the%20National%20League%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99s%20parallel%20National%20Unity%20Government%20(NUG).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEAOs%20have%20enjoyed%20autonomy%20following%20ceasefire%20agreements%20with%20the%20military.%20Not%20all%20have%20submitted%20to%20ceasefire%20arrangements%2C%20though.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20powerful%20Arakan%20Army%20(AA)%20which%20operates%20in%20Rakhine%2C%20Chin%20and%20Arakan%20states%20broke%20its%20ceasefire%20in%20November%20last%20year%20and%20went%20on%20the%20offensive%20to%20defeat%20the%20junta%20in%20these%20two%20states.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20Rohingyas%20may%20have%20joined%20AA.%20The%20Chin%20National%20Army%20also%20operates%20in%20this%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmyanmar-junta-arakan-army-resistance%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20Armed%20Resistance%20Is%20Testing%20Myanmar%20Junta%E2%80%99s%20Grip%20on%20Power%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20a%20look%20back.%20On%20September%207%2C%202022%2C%20the%20Special%20Advisory%20Council%20of%20International%20Experts%20Supporting%20Democracy%20released%20a%20paper%20which%20showed%20that%20the%20junta%20control%2072%20of%20333%20major%20towns%20and%2017%25%20of%20land%20area.%20The%20EAOs%20were%20reportedly%20controlling%2052%25%20of%20territory%20while%2023%25%20was%20contested.%20Those%20were%20early%20days.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20major%20offensives%20were%20launched%20in%20October%20and%20November%20last%20year%20called%201027%20and%201111%2C%20(the%20last%20two%20figures%20denoting%20month%20and%20next%20two%20figures%20the%20date%20of%20operation)%20by%20an%20alliance%20of%20three%20EAOs%20along%20with%20PDF%20and%20militias.%20These%20operations%20stretched%20from%20Rakhine%20in%20the%20south%C2%A0%20to%20all%20of%20the%20northeast%20up%20till%20Lashio.%20The%20AA%20seized%20control%20of%20territory%20bordering%20India%20including%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20pockets%20in%20Mandalay%20and%20Bago.%20The%20biggest%20setback%20for%20the%20junta%20was%20in%20the%20northern%20Shan%20state%20and%20Kokang%20Special%20Region%20where%20it%20lost%20Laukkai%2C%20one%20of%20its%20seven%20operational%20command%20centres.%20The%20Myanmar%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20Army%20(MNDAA)%20which%20spearheaded%20attacks%20in%20the%20north%2C%20scored%20major%20successes%20and%20closed%20down%20five%20border%20trade%20centres%20and%20crossing%20points%20with%20China.%20A%20number%20of%20Chinese%20living%20in%20the%20north%20had%20to%20flee%20to%20Yunnan%20(China).%20General%20Peng%20Deren%2C%20commander%20of%20the%20MNDAA%2C%20said%20wresting%20control%20of%20the%20north%20from%20the%20junta%20and%20restoring%20its%20writ%20to%20end%20criminal%20activities%20was%20sweet%20revenge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chinese%2C%20after%20a%20series%20of%20negotiations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fmyanmar-china-ceasefire-guerrillas-b60aa673a2fc38cd04e7dd781e3625c5%5C%22%3Ebrokered%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20the%20junta%20on%20January%2012%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20some%20EAOs%20in%20MNDAA%20did%20not%20acknowledge.%20Clearly%20these%20offensives%20in%20the%20north%20and%20northeast%20could%20not%20have%20been%20launched%20without%20Chinese%20complicity.%20For%20some%20time%20now%2C%20the%20Chinese%20have%20wanted%20to%20stop%20and%20eliminate%20various%20drug%20and%20gambling%20rackets%20that%20have%20been%20going%20on%20with%20the%20knowledge%20and%20possible%20cooperation%20of%20the%20military.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJunta%20retaliation%20to%20its%20losses%20has%20come%20mainly%20through%20artillery%20shelling%2C%20strafing%20by%20helicopters%20and%20jets%20of%20towns%20that%20it%20evacuated%20after%20being%20outgunned.%20Many%20Brigadier%20Generals%2C%20Colonels%20and%20soldiers%20surrendered%20without%20fighting.%20Sui%20Lee%20Wei%20writing%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20December%2023%2C%20reported%20that%20around%204%2C500%20(this%20figure%20often%20varies%20and%20rises%20to%206%2C000%20in%20some%20accounts)%20personnel%20could%20have%20defected%20among%20a%20total%20of%2021%2C000%20estimated%20casualties.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20junta%20does%20not%20reveal%20its%20losses%20but%20experts%20estimate%20that%20Junta%20strength%20is%20still%20around%20300%2C000%20to%20400%2C000%20soldiers%20with%20modern%20weapons.%20They%20are%20encountering%20difficulties%20in%20making%20up%20shortfalls%20as%20last%20year%2C%20only%2083%20cadets%20joined%20the%20defence%20academy%20compared%20to%201%2C000%20in%202022.%20On%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20day%2C%20coup%20General%20Min%20Aung%20Hlaing%20issued%20honorary%20titles%20for%20combatants%20and%20praised%20the%20junta%20forces%20for%20their%20dedication.%20Hlaing%20offered%20a%20political%20resolution%20to%20resistance%20forces%20asking%20them%20to%20stop%20fighting%20a%20war%20they%20could%20not%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fembed%3Fpb%3D!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d29952.794809809635!2d93.1128213214015!3d20.213192149322396!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x30b0fed487d693c5%253A0xb745b464807ad06d!2sPauktaw%252C%2520Myanmar%2520(Burma)!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1707042115693!5m2!1sen!2sin%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22450%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20big%20win%20for%20EAOs%20was%20by%20AA%20in%20Pauktaw%20close%20to%20Sittwe%2C%20where%20India%20operates%20its%20deep%20sea%20port%20for%20implementing%20its%20Act%20East%20policy%20that%20includes%20constructing%20infrastructure%20like%20the%20multi-modal%20Kaladan%20river%20project.%20Paletwa%20town%20which%20rests%20on%20Kaladan%20was%20captured%20by%20AA%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20is%20key%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20trilateral%20highway%20from%20Moreh%20in%20India%20to%20Moe%20Sat%20(Thailand)%20passing%20through%20Sagaing%20region.%20So%20now%2C%20AA%20has%20become%20the%20key%20interlocutor%20for%20New%20Delhi%20to%20ensure%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20its%20border%20in%20Rakhine%20and%20Arakan%20states%20and%20Sagaing%20region%2C%20the%20areas%20it%20controls.%20New%20Delhi%20should%20recalibrate%20its%20policy%20towards%20the%20junta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20naval%20base%20at%20Sittwe%20under%20threat%2C%20(members%20of%20the%20Pauktaw%20garrison%20are%20known%20to%20have%20escaped%20by%20boat%20on%20January%2019)%20the%20junta%20has%20lost%20control%20of%20an%20arc%20of%20territory%20covering%20Myanmar%20borders%20with%20India%20and%20China%20including%20loss%20of%20trade%20with%20China.%20Fighting%20had%20crept%20towards%20Junta%20headquarters%20at%20its%20new%20capital%20Naypitaw%20but%20is%20still%20some%20200%20km%20to%20its%20north.%20Most%20of%20the%20central%20and%20southern%20regions%20as%20also%20bordering%20Thailand%20is%20under%20Naypitaw%20control.%20The%20Bamar%20heartland%20is%20the%20Yangon%20valley.%20The%20junta%E2%80%99s%20naval%20and%20air%20bases%20are%20in%20this%20region.%20The%20losses%20by%20any%20count%20are%20significant%20and%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20strategic%20shift%20in%20direction%20of%20civil%20war%20and%20in%20relative%20balance%20of%20power%20resulting%20from%20tactical%20defeats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20resistance%E2%80%99s%20successes%20are%20outstanding%2C%20they%20do%20not%20represent%20military%20victory.%20The%20resistance%20would%20have%20to%20capture%20a%20major%20air%20base%20and%20secure%20key%20pockets%20in%20Yangon%20to%20pose%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20junta.%20Further%2C%20despite%20desertions%20and%20defections%2C%20cohesion%20of%20military%20formations%20who%20realise%20they%20have%20high%20stakes%20in%20the%20war%20are%20intact%3A%20so%20are%20the%20elite%20divisions%20not%20committed%20in%20battle.%20But%20the%20next%20round%20of%20fighting%20will%20be%20in%20and%20around%20Sittwe%20and%20that%20may%20be%20the%20clincher.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fthree-years-of-coup-in-myanmar-what-explains-indias-pro-junta-position%5C%22%3EThree%20Years%20of%20Coup%20in%20Myanmar%3A%20What%20Explains%20India%E2%80%99s%20Pro-Junta%20Position%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEAOs%20in%20the%20resistance%20have%20dominant%20interests%20mainly%20confined%20to%20their%20states%20or%20regions%20and%20seek%20bigger%20influence%20with%20Naypitaw%20to%20enhance%20their%20autonomy.%20General%20Deren%E2%80%99s%20New%20Year%20statement%20indicated%20that%20MNDAA%20has%20achieved%20its%20objective.%20A%20resistance%20alliance%20that%20will%20venture%20into%20the%20heartland%20is%20unlikely%20to%20take%20shape.%20Further%2C%20EAOs%20have%C2%A0%20political%20differences%20though%20they%20can%20cooperate%20militarily%2C%20but%20locally.%20Although%20the%20current%20initiative%20and%20momentum%20are%20with%20the%20resistance%2C%20their%20differences%20with%20NUG%20is%20another%20impediment%20to%20military%20unity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%2C%20which%20has%20big%20political%20and%20economic%20interests%20in%20Myanmar%20will%20not%20allow%20defenestration%20of%20junta%20forces.%20Along%20with%20Russia%20it%20will%20double%20down%20on%20providing%20military%20and%20economic%20support%20to%20Junta.%20Beijing%20has%20strong%20links%20and%20influence%20with%20EAOs%20like%20AA%20whom%20it%20has%20been%20supplying%20weapons.%20China%20will%20be%20a%20key%20actor%20in%20any%20long%20term%20political%20solution%2C%20not%20just%20because%20it%20is%20the%20dominant%20external%20player%20but%20also%20due%20to%20its%20huge%20political%20and%20economic%20investments.%20While%20it%20has%20a%20love-hate%20relationship%20with%20the%20military%20it%20also%20enjoyed%20friendly%20and%20stable%20relations%20with%20the%20democratic%20polity%20post%202011%20during%20the%20hybrid%20rule%20era.%20China%20will%20want%20a%20cohesive%20Army%20to%20keep%20the%20country%20together%20as%20it%20has%20since%201948.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20its%20back%20to%20the%20wall%2C%20the%20junta%20has%20no%20good%20options%20to%20break%20the%20stalemate.%20Two%20main%20choices%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Ea)%20A%20negotiated%20political%20solution%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fhow-aseans-failed-five-point-consensus-has-let-down-the-people-of-myanmar%5C%22%3EASEAN%E2%80%99s%20Five-Point%20Consensus%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20time%20is%20not%20on%20its%20side%20the%20junta%20will%20try%20to%20secure%20an%20end%20to%20fighting%20%E2%80%93%20a%20ceasefire%20followed%20by%20cessation%20of%20hostilities.%20Although%20the%20balance%20of%20advantage%20is%20with%20the%20resistance%2C%20Junta%20forces%20are%20as%20yet%20invincible.%20But%20a%20political%20solution%20acceptable%20to%20the%20NUG%20and%20democratic%20forces%20must%20result%20in%20a%20significantly%20diminished%20role%20for%20military%20in%20governance%20and%20politics.%20For%20example%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20represented%20by%20a%20political%20party%20with%2025%25%20seat%20reservation%3B%20ministers%20of%20defence%2C%20interior%20and%20border%20%E2%80%93%20hitherto%20from%20military%20%E2%80%93%20must%20be%20civilians%3B%20and%20the%202008%20military-drafted%20constitution%20suspended.%20This%20climbdown%20by%20military%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20to%20negotiate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3Eb)%20The%20second%20option%20is%20to%20keep%20fighting%20and%20broker%20ceasefire%20deals%20with%20EAOs%20in%20order%20to%20break%20the%20unity%20among%20the%20resistance.%20The%20junta%20cannot%20afford%20to%20lose%20the%20war%20as%20that%20holds%20the%20spectre%20of%20generals%20facing%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20at%20the%20Hague%20over%20allegations%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Rohingya%20in%202019%20and%20Burmans%20during%20the%20civil%20war.%20The%20United%20Nations%20has%20in%20its%20contingency%20planning%20cupboard%20for%20fragile%20and%20failing%20states%2C%20detailed%20plans%20for%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20day%20after%E2%80%9D.%20I%20have%20seen%20one%20for%20Afghanistan%20in%202015%20when%20the%20end%20game%20was%20being%20explored.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAshok%20K.%20Mehta%2C%20a%20major%20general%2C%20is%20a%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Defence%20Planning%20Staff%2C%20now%20the%20Integrated%20Defence%20Staff.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707042592000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F10235624%2FProtest_in_Myanmar_against_Military_Coup_14-Feb-2021_05.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fthe-past-present-and-future-of-resistance-in-myanmar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Will%20the%20junta%20keep%20fighting%20and%20broker%20ceasefire%20deals%20with%20resistance%20groups%3F%20Or%20will%20it%20try%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20to%20broker%20an%20end%20to%20fighting%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fthe-past-present-and-future-of-resistance-in-myanmar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20may%20continue%20status-quo%20on%20short-term%20lending%20rate%2C%20say%20experts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707042530000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F02%2Ffull%2F1698902779-8176.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-may-continue-status-quo-on-short-term-lending-rate-say-experts-124020400319_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RBI%20Governor-headed%20Monetary%20Policy%20Committee%20(MPC)%20will%20start%20its%20three-day%20deliberations%20on%20February%206.%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20will%20announce%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20six-member%20panel%20on%20February%208%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-may-continue-status-quo-on-short-term-lending-rate-say-experts-124020400319_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-may-continue-status-quo-on-short-term-lending-rate-say-experts-124020400319_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Frbi-may-continue-status-quo-on-short-term-lending-rate-say-experts-124020400319_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22There%E2%80%99s%20Temple%20Politics%20Where%20You%20Least%20Expect%20It%20%E2%80%93%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20for%20One%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150323%2FChapter-5-photograph-2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2023%2C%202017%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20three%20years%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20give%20the%20historic%20verdict%20on%20Ram%20temple%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Gangajalghati%20subdivision%20of%20Bankura%2C%20an%20old%20autorickshaw%20passed%20through%20the%20dusty%20village%20road.%20It%20was%20being%20chased%20by%20Santhali%20kids%20from%20Shiulibona%20village%20and%20as%20it%20sped%20up%2C%20I%20heard%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20grand%20inauguration%20of%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20near%20Jamshala%20village%20the%20next%20day.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKids%20were%20excited%2C%20so%20was%20my%20key%20informant%20from%20Jamshala%20Shyamal%20Mandi%2C%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20in%20their%20village%20instead%20of%20Shiulibona.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20I%20met%20Rabon%20Shoren%2C%20a%20middle-aged%20tribal%20gentleman%2C%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98Samayita%20Math%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20a%20quasi-religious%20Hindu%20centre%20in%20Shiulibona.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamayita%20Math%20runs%20an%20open%20prayer%20hall%20and%20has%20installed%20a%20road-side%20temple-like%20structure%20in%20the%20village%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Marang%20Buru.%20Approximately%20one%20kilometre%20from%20the%20Susunia%20hills%20is%20the%20Santhali%20Disham%20shrine%20%E2%80%93%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20religio-political%20hierarchy%20of%20the%20Santhal%20tradition.%20The%20shrine%20has%20three%20erected%20stones%20and%2C%20now%20aided%20with%20a%20submersible%20pump%20set%2C%20an%20overhead%20tank%20for%20the%20visitors%20to%20have%20access%20to%20basic%20amenities.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20are%20recent%20developments%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rabon%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20October%2015%2C%202020%2C%20while%20driving%20from%20Purulia%20towards%20Ranchi%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20stay%20at%20the%20Pathersathi%20hotel%20in%20Chashmore%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20and%20run%20by%20local%20self%20help%20groups.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20get%20rooms%20as%20not%20many%20were%20travelling%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20On%20my%20way%2C%20I%20encountered%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%20at%20each%20village%20we%20crossed.%20My%20travel%20partner%20Sukumar%20Hansda%2C%20a%20local%20young%20guy%2C%20saw%20my%20curiosity%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20they%20kept%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%2C%20then%20they%20constructed%20a%20plinth%20and%20then%20a%20temple.%E2%80%9D%20On%20being%20asked%20who%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20were%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindus%E2%80%A6%20they%20are%20many.%20Bajrang%20dal%2C%20Durgashakti%2C%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram..%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhunger-and-broken-promises-in-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3EOnce%20a%20Maoist%20Hotbed%2C%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Jungle%20Mahal%20Is%20Now%20Battling%20Hunger%20and%20Anger%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20realised%20that%20the%20hotel%20where%20we%20were%20staying%20was%20located%20exactly%20between%20two%20such%20temples%20%E2%80%93%20one%20at%20Dumardih%20Upar%20Para%20and%20another%20one%20at%20Velaidihi.%20There%20was%20another%20a%20little%20inside%20the%20village%20at%20Tanasi.%20All%20three%20were%20constructed%20almost%20overnight%20in%202019%2C%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20parliamentary%20elections.%20Before%20that%20they%20were%20open%20installations%20of%20Hanuman%20idols.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20three%20villages%20have%20mixed%20population%2C%20predominated%20by%20Hindus%2C%20a%20few%20hamlets%20of%20Santhal%20people%20and%20a%20small%20ghettoised%20Muslim%20settlement%20on%20the%20northern%20side.%20The%20three%20temples%20ran%20%3Cem%3EHanuman%20Chalisa%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamayana%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20a%20loudspeaker%20that%20were%20directed%20towards%20the%20Muslim%20settlement.%20Visibly%20afraid%2C%20none%20of%20the%20Muslims%2C%20during%20my%20first%20visit%2C%20said%20anything%20about%20the%20temple.%20They%20maintained%20that%20such%20constructions%20or%20the%20loudspeaker%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20noisy%20even%20to%20my%20urban%20ear%20habituated%20with%20everyday%20cacophony%2C%20did%20not%20affect%20their%20everyday%20life.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20my%20subsequent%20visits%20to%20the%20villages%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20all%20three%20temples%20were%20constructed%20by%20taking%20subscription%20money%20from%20the%20villagers%20which%20included%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Santhals.%20People%20belonging%20to%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%20from%20Joypur%20appointed%20village%20level%20volunteers%20for%20temple%20construction%20and%20now%20they%20are%20run%20by%20temple%20committees.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEvenings%20are%20well%20spent%20near%20the%20temple%20site%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Emahant%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chief%20priest)%20worships%20Ram%20and%20Hanuman%2C%20narrating%20stories%20of%20the%20great%20power.%20Villagers%20are%20also%20told%20that%20in%20a%20remote%20past%2C%20they%20protected%20local%20kings%20and%20their%20beautiful%20daughters%20from%20getting%20abducted%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98ruthless%20Muslim%20rulers%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EBackground%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%202008-2011%2C%20Jungle%20Mahal%20(Bankura%2C%20Purulia%20and%20West%20Midnapore%20and%20Jhargram%20districts%20of%20West%20Bengal)%20had%20seen%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.satp.org%2Fdatasheet-terrorist-attack%2Ffatalities%2Findia-maoistinsurgency-westbengal%5C%22%3Ebloodiest%20episodes%20of%20violence%20in%20independent%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20total%20of%20505%20civilians%20getting%20killed%20during%20the%20period%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBased%20on%20a%20longitudinal%2C%20mixed%20method%20study%20in%20a%20recently%20published%20journal%20article%20we%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs12116-023-09389-w%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20the%20rebel%20align%20party%20wins%20immediately%20after%20the%20civil%20war%2C%20their%20continuation%20depends%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20violence%20used%20by%20the%20rebel%20groups.%20In%20case%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal.%20the%20sudden%20disappearance%20of%20Maoist%20rebels%2C%20especially%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2FKishenji-killed-in-encounter%2Farticle13499991.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20death%20of%20Kishen%20ji%20%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20their%20counterparts%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20or%20CPI(M)-controlled%20Harmad%20Bahini%2C%20led%20to%20an%20organisational%20vacuum.%20Such%20vacuum%20was%20never%20compensated%20and%20the%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20government%20did%20what%20is%20termed%20as%20hyper-development%20using%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1080%2F14672715.2017.1415762%5C%22%3E%20non-elected%20arms%20of%20the%20local%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-rss-hindutva-bengal-nationalist-icons%5C%22%3EBJP%20and%20the%20Art%20of%20Selling%20Hindutva%20Nationalism%20to%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20precisely%20in%20this%20moment%20of%20absence%20of%20organisations%20that%20Jungle%20Mahal%20saw%20a%20proliferation%20of%20Hanuman%20idols%20and%20temples.%20Coordinated%20precisely%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F886576%2Fground-report-how-the-bjp-is-gaining-in-west-bengals-one-time-maoist-stronghold-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3EEkal%20Vidyalayas%20and%20Vanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%20soon%20ventured%20on%20the%20newly%20constructed%20roads%20laid%20by%20the%20TMC.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20everyday%20image%20of%20Hindutva%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETemple%20politics%20at%20the%20grassroots%20has%20been%20rather%20successful%20in%20translating%20popular%20support%20to%20gain%20electoral%20dividend%20for%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20The%20four%20major%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%20were%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20with%20astonishing%20increase%20in%20electoral%20support%20base.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20vote%20share%20increased%20by%2014.4%25%20in%20Bankura%2C%20Purulia%20(42.1%25)%2C%20Bishnupur%20(32.1%25)%20and%20Jhargram%20(34.8%25)%20as%20compared%20to%202014.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20would%20be%20immature%20to%20associate%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20win%20solely%20to%20temple%20politics.%20There%20are%20reasons%20related%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F886576%2Fground-report-how-the-bjp-is-gaining-in-west-bengals-one-time-maoist-stronghold-jungle-mahal%5C%22%3ETMC%E2%80%99s%20failures%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20However%2C%20temple%20politics%20does%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20uniting%20an%20otherwise%20diverse%20pool%20of%20voters%20against%20a%20common%20enemy%2C%20the%20Muslims%2C%20for%20a%20common%20cause%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98search%20for%20the%20true%20soul%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20and%20for%20a%20common%20insecurity%20that%20%E2%80%98Hindus%20are%20in%20danger%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.routledge.com%2FDemocracy-and-Social-Cleavage-in-India-Ethnography-of-Riots-Everyday-Politics%2FNath%2Fp%2Fbook%2F9781032226453%5C%22%3Eongoing%20ethnographic%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20find%20out%20people%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20in%20Hindutva%20ideology%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20If%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faamrabharatbarsha.com%2Fwelcome%2Fcategory%2FConflict%2520%26amp%3B%2520Co-existence%2520Reports%5C%22%3Eeveryday%20polarisation%20through%20low-intense%20riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20resulted%20in%20wide%20spread%20of%20fundamentalist%20sentiments%20among%20both%20the%20communities%20is%20one%20of%20the%20mechanisms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ijcv.org%2Findex.php%2Fijcv%2Farticle%2Fview%2F3119%5C%22%3Einvented%20traditions%20is%20another%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20parallel%20to%20this%20has%20been%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20image%20among%20the%20villagers%20of%20the%20remote%20villages%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal.%20Before%20the%20invention%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%2C%20which%20frequently%20results%20in%20riots%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0these%20temples%20served%20as%20the%20primary%20%E2%80%98logo%E2%80%99%20and%20entry%20point%20to%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbengal-ram-navami-bihar-violence%5C%22%3E%20grand%20Hindutva%20model%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20287px)%2085vw%2C%20287px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22287%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150535%2FConclusions-photograph-1.jpg%20900w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695661%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22383%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20shrine%20in%20Kolkata%20where%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%20can%20be%20seen.%20Photo%3A%20Author%20provided%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20while%20every%20village%20of%20Jungle%20Mahal%20region%20has%20a%20Hanuman%20temple%2C%20bright%20orange%20flags%20and%20relatively%20smaller%20Hanuman%20idols%20are%20kept%20in%20the%20pre-existing%20shrines%20of%20Shitala%20and%20Manasha%20cult%20which%20has%20been%20worshipped%20by%20the%20villagers%20since%20time%20immemorial.%20Spatial%20and%20boundary%20principles%20are%20attached%20to%20the%20traditional%20shrines%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshodhganga.inflibnet.ac.in%2Fhandle%2F10603%2F18159%5C%22%3E%20their%20archaeological%20continuity%20and%20significance%20is%20enormous%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENeedless%20to%20say%2C%20these%20have%20created%20a%20special%20space%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20the%20people%20who%20worship%20them.%20It%20was%20the%20everyday%20form%20of%20benevolent%20local%20goddess%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20protectors%20of%20people%20from%20snakebites%20and%20infectious%20diseases.%20They%20were%20never%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20These%20goddesses%20are%20usually%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.2307%2F1177724%5C%22%3Eworshipped%20by%20the%20women%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20these%20villages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20men%20placing%20a%20Hanuman%20idol%20next%20to%20them%20is%20not%20only%20an%20intrusion%20of%20masculinity%20within%20the%20feminine%20sphere%2C%20but%20also%20an%20introduction%20of%20the%20masculine%20Hindutva%20thought%20in%20the%20folk%20tradition%20of%20village%20deities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20several%20villages%2C%20where%20Hanuman%20idols%20are%20placed%20in%20existing%20sacred%20groves%2C%20villagers%2C%20including%20the%20women%20haven%E2%80%99t%20found%20it%20unusual.%20Hanuman%E2%80%99s%20stories%20are%20being%20narrated%20through%20oral%20traditions%20and%20in%20school-level%20texts.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20having%20Pavanputra%20in%20the%20village%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Edevta%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20we%20should%20worship%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20women%20from%20Gangajalghati%20said%20during%20a%20casual%20conversation%20among%20the%20villagers%20during%20my%20visit%20last%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20is%20expanding%20its%20base%20among%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%20because%20of%20the%20narrative%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20has%20been%20so%20successful%20in%20building.%20We%20know%20that%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20not%20where%20they%20would%20stop%2C%20perhaps%20it%20is%20just%20the%20beginning%20of%20their%20plan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20And%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20temple%20politics%20in%20Jungle%20Mahal%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20BJP%20in%20bagging%20several%20constituencies%2C%20is%20just%20one%20small%20part%20of%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20groves%20and%20temples%20that%20were%20decked%20with%20bright%20orange%20flags%20of%20angry%20hanuman%20and%20Ram%20images%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20January%2022%20have%20further%20made%20an%20impact%20into%20the%20cultural-cognitive%20dimensions%20of%20these%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESuman%20Nath%20teaches%20anthropology%20at%20Dr.%20APJ%20Abdul%20Kalam%20Government%20College%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%20and%20Social%20Cleavage%20in%20India%20Ethnography%20of%20Riots%2C%20Everyday%20Politics%20and%20Communalism%20in%20West%20Bengal%20c.%202012%E2%80%932021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040845000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150323%2FChapter-5-photograph-2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftheres-temple-politics-where-you-least-expect-it-bengals-jungle-mahal-for-one%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20the%20invention%20of%20Ram%20Navami%20processions%2C%20which%20frequently%20results%20in%20riots%2C%C2%A0these%20temples%20served%20as%20the%20primary%20'logo'%20and%20entry%20point%20to%20the%20grand%20Hindutva%20model%20in%20West%20Bengal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftheres-temple-politics-where-you-least-expect-it-bengals-jungle-mahal-for-one%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Did%20Puja%20at%20Gyanvapi'%3A%20Now%2C%20BJP's%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Uma%20Bharti%20Back%20Hindu%20Plaintiffs'%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04152216%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Aligning%20with%20the%20claims%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%2C%20at%20least%20two%20senior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20have%20publicly%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20performed%20puja%20facing%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20mosque%20or%20in%20its%20basement%20before%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Varanasi%20administration%2C%20executing%20the%20controversial%20orders%20of%20a%20district%20court%2C%20supervised%20the%20installation%20of%20idols%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20inside%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20arranged%20prayer%20rituals%20by%20a%20Hindu%20priest%20there.%20The%20administration%20has%20also%20cut%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20steel%20barricade%20that%20secures%20the%20mosque%20to%20allow%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20Hindu%20priests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20have%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20and%20baseless%E2%80%9D%20the%20claims%20by%20a%20Hindu%20plaintiff%20that%20idols%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20existed%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20they%20used%20to%20be%20worshipped%20by%20his%20ancestors%20till%20the%20mosque%20was%20barricaded%20in%20December%201993%20following%20Supreme%20Court%20orders%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Lucknow%20on%20February%203%2C%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20claimed%20that%20till%201993%2C%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20%E2%80%9CVyas%20ji%20ka%20tehkhana%E2%80%9D%20was%20open%20and%20people%20would%20offer%20prayers%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20had%20the%20good%20fortune%20of%20doing%20%E2%80%98darshan%E2%80%99%20there.%20But%20in%201993%20it%20was%20stopped%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maurya%20said%20at%20the%20%E2%80%9CShri%20Ram%20Darbar%E2%80%9D%2C%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20a%20newly-launched%20right-wing%20platform%20Shri%20Guru%20Vasishtha%20Nyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaurya%2C%20who%20described%20the%20puja%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%E2%80%9D%20event%2C%20also%20said%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20of%20which%20he%20was%20a%20part%2C%20wanted%20it%20could%20have%20opened%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20for%20Hindu%20prayers%20but%20it%20chose%20to%20not%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20as%20well%20as%20members%20of%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%20claimed%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Hindu%20deities%20near%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque%20was%20stopped%20during%20the%20rule%20of%20then%20chief%20minister%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%201993.%20The%20saffron%20party%20has%20for%20years%20tried%20to%20appease%20Hindu%20voters%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20firing%20on%20%3Cem%3Ekar%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Esevaks%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201990%20when%20they%20were%20attempting%20to%20demolish%20the%20Babri%20Masjid.%20With%20a%20court%20in%20Varanasi%20handing%20over%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20to%20Hindus%20for%20puja%2C%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20actively%20trying%20to%20drag%20the%20main%20opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20into%20the%20controversy%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20further%20polarise%20Hindu%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20double%20engine%20government%20working%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%20with%20impartiality.%20What%20happened%20during%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20in%201993%2C%20we%20could%20have%20%5Baltered%20it%5D%20after%20we%20formed%20the%20government%20in%202017%20but%20we%20did%20not%20do%20any%20such%20thing.%20The%20shiv%20bhakts%20and%20plaintiffs%20took%20the%20shelter%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Maurya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpuja-to-continue-in-gyanvapi-basement-no-hc-relief-feb-6%5C%22%3ENo%20Immediate%20HC%20Relief%2C%20Puja%20to%20Continue%20Inside%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Basement%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUma%20Bharti%20and%20Alok%20Kumar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20Maurya%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20district%20court%20order%2C%20former%20union%20minister%20Uma%20Bharti%20%E2%80%93%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recognisable%20women%20of%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20of%20the%20early%201990s%20%E2%80%93%20also%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20worshipped%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%20inscribed%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20decision%20on%20Gyanvapi%20is%20pleasant.%20I%20have%20myself%20worshipped%20the%20idols%20inscribed%20on%20the%20walls%20of%20Gyanvapi%20in%201993%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bharti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20sought%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfinal%20solution%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20dispute%20and%20said%20that%20the%20land%20on%20which%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20the%20Shahi%20Eidgah%20Masjid%20in%20Mathura%20stand%2C%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20Hindus%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20temples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20VHP%20too%20has%20made%20a%20similar%20claim%20in%20public%20declaring%20the%20southern%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctemple.%E2%80%9D%20The%20far-right%20organization%20affiliated%20to%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20said%20that%20till%201993%2C%20%E2%80%9Cregular%20puja%20archana%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20deities%20was%20going%20on%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%201993%2C%20the%20administration%20had%2C%20in%20an%20arbitrary%20action%2C%20barricaded%20the%20area%2C%20prohibited%20the%20Hindus%20from%20going%20to%20the%20temple%20and%20stopped%20the%20puja%20archana%2C%E2%80%9D%20VHP%20international%20working%20president%20Alok%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fjudge-hands-over-gyanvapi-basement-to-hindus%5C%22%3EA%20Day%20Before%20Retiring%2C%20Varanasi%20Judge%20Hands%20Over%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20Basement%20to%20Hindus%20For%20Worship%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20suit%20filed%20in%202022%2C%20Rakhi%20Singh%20and%20four%20other%20Hindu%20women%2C%20made%20a%20similar%20claim%20that%20the%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20were%20performing%20daily%20puja%20and%20worship%20of%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20within%20the%20%E2%80%9Cold%20temple%E2%80%9D%20continuously%20till%201990%20when%20the%20state%20government%20in%20view%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20movement%20put%20restrictions%20on%20the%20daily%20puja.%20Since%201993%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20under%20the%20oral%20orders%20of%20the%20state%20government%20allowed%20devotees%20to%20perform%20puja%20only%20once%20a%20year%2C%20on%20the%204th%20day%20of%20Vasantik%20Navratra%20in%20Chaitra%2C%20Rakhi%20Singh%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20opposition%20in%20UP%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20so%20far%20not%20openly%20rebutted%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20VHP%20and%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20district%20administration%20started%20puja%20inside%20the%20basement%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20February%201%2C%20SP%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20criticized%20the%20developments%2C%20saying%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20we%3Cbr%3E%5Cnare%20seeing%20now%20is%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20due%20process%20and%20prevent%20any%20legal%20recourse%20that%20can%20be%20taken.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%2C%20while%20stressing%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20district%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20administration%20to%20comply%20with%20its%20order%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20process%20had%20to%20be%20maintained%20while%20following%20any%20court%20order.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20was%20asked%20by%20journalists%20outside%20Parliament%20on%20February%202%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20had%20stopped%20puja%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Mosque%20during%20his%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20irritated%20Ram%20Gopal%20Yadav%20responded%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20is%20saying%20Mulayam%20Singh%20stopped%20prayers%3F%20Only%20idiots%20can%20say%20like%20this%20(%3Cem%3Esic%3C%2Fem%3E).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20argued%20that%20court%20decisions%20were%20not%20always%20correct%20or%20absolute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20absolutely%20correct.%20Nothing%20is%20absolutely%20perfect.%20Every%20decision%2C%20for%20one%20side%20it%20is%20right%2C%20for%20another%20side%20it%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funderstanding-the-gyanvapi-mosque-dispute-what-does-the-places-of-worship-act-say%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Case%3A%20What%20Does%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20Say%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%20Comittee%20Varanasi%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%2C%20in%20a%20new%20statement%20condemned%20the%20action%20by%20the%20court%20and%20administration%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone-sided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20that%20we%20will%20fight%20for%20the%20protection%20and%20security%20of%20the%20Jama%20Masjid%20Gyanvapi%20till%20our%20last%20breath%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maulana%20Abdul%20Batin%20Nomani%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Committee%2C%20said%20in%20a%20note%20addressed%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Masjid%20committee%20has%20maintained%2C%20inside%20and%20outside%20court%2C%20that%20question%20of%20stopping%20Hindus%20from%20conducting%20puja%20from%20December%201993%20did%20not%20arise%20as%20no%20member%20of%20the%20Vyas%20family%20ever%20carried%20out%20puja%20in%20the%20cellar.%20No%20idol%20was%20ever%20present%20inside%20the%20basement%2C%20the%20committee%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20it%20had%20always%20been%20under%20their%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES.%20M.%20Yasin%2C%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20Anjuman%20Intezamia%20Masajid%2C%20dismissed%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20that%20they%20had%20offered%20prayers%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20or%20facing%20its%20walls%20till%20at%20least%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20lies.%20There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying.%20No%20such%20puja%20has%20ever%20happened.%20The%20plaintiff%20did%20not%20provide%20any%20evidence%20in%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yasin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20some%20people%20did%20try%20to%20offer%20puja%20to%20%E2%80%9CMaa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%9D%20but%20they%20were%20chased%20away%20by%20the%20administration%2C%20said%20he.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYasin%20also%20questioned%20the%20district%20administration%E2%80%99s%20act%20of%20installing%20new%20idols%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20mosque%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%20when%20the%20district%20court%20had%20on%20January%2031%20only%20directed%20the%20administration%20to%20conduct%20the%20puja%20and%20%E2%80%9Crag-bhog%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cidols%E2%80%9D%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%20through%20a%20pujari%20appointed%20by%20the%20Shri%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Temple%20Trust%2C%20which%20manages%20the%20adjoining%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20order%20to%20go%20and%20keep%20new%20idols%20there%20when%20the%20plaintiff%20had%20already%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20present%20inside.%20How%20come%20the%20ASI%20did%20not%20find%20the%20idols%20during%20its%20survey%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Yasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20compared%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20surreptitious%20planting%20of%20idols%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20inside%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%201949%20with%20the%20support%20of%20the%20then%20district%20magistrate%20K.K%20Nair%20who%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Sangh%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20both%20cases%2C%20the%20idols%20were%20planted%20surreptitiously%20in%20the%20night.%20In%201949%2C%20the%20administration%20facilitated%20it.%20In%202024%2C%20the%20administration%20themselves%20carried%20out%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yasin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fkashi-mathura-baaki-hain-why-the-ayodhya-verdict-wont-offer-any-respite-from-saffron-hatred%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Kashi-Mathura%20Baaqi%20Hain%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20the%20Ayodhya%20Verdict%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Offer%20Any%20Respite%20From%20Saffron%20Hatred%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBall%20in%20court%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20prayers%20inside%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20will%20continue%20at%20least%20till%20February%206%20as%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20on%20Friday%20did%20not%20grant%20any%20relief%20to%20the%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20district%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20of%20handing%20over%20the%20basement%20to%20Hindus%20for%20puja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20directed%20the%20mosque%20management%20committee%20to%20file%20a%20fresh%2C%20amended%20appeal%20against%20the%20district%20court%20order%20and%20said%20it%20would%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20February%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20judge%20A.%20K%20Vishvesha%20on%20January%2031%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20puja%20and%20other%20Hindu%20activities%20inside%20the%20southern%20tehkhana%20(cellar)%20of%20the%20mosque%20within%20seven%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Varanasi%20court%20order%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20in%20its%20survey%20report%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20claimed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20Hindu%20temple%E2%80%9D%20existed%20there%20prior%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20existing%20structure%20i.e%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20temple%20were%20modified%20and%20used%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Islamic%20place%20of%20worship.%20The%20masjid%20committee%20is%20yet%20to%20submit%20a%20detailed%20objection%20to%20the%20report%20but%20has%20disagreed%20with%20the%20conclusions%20of%20the%20ASI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20passed%20the%20order%20on%20an%20application%20filed%20by%20a%20local%20priest%20Shailendra%20Kumar%20Pathak%20of%20the%20Acharya%20Ved%20Vyas%20Peeth%20temple%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20rights%20to%20worship%20the%20Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%20and%20other%20alleged%20visible%20and%20invisible%20deities%20he%20claimed%20were%20in%20the%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretakers%20of%20the%20mosque%20rejected%20all%20claims%20made%20by%20Pathak%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20inside%20the%20previously-sealed%20cellar%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20used%20to%20carry%20out%20puja%20inside%20the%20cellar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Vishvesha%2C%20however%2C%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Hindu%20plaintiff%2C%20and%20directed%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20make%20necessary%20iron%20fencing%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20puja.%20The%20district%20magistrate%20had%20on%20January%2024%20completed%20the%20process%20of%20taking%20over%20the%20cellar%20after%20the%20court%20on%20January%2017%20directed%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20to%20keep%20the%20cellar%20secure%20and%20appointed%20him%20as%20the%20receiver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20application%2C%20Pathak%20claimed%20that%20there%20were%20idols%20kept%20in%20the%20southern%20cellar%20of%20the%20mosque%20and%20that%20his%20ancestors%20as%20priests%20conducted%20worship%20of%20the%20idols%20kept%20there.%20However%2C%20Pathak%20further%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9CPujari%20Vyas%20ji%2C%E2%80%9D%20or%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20his%20maternal%20grandfather%2C%20was%20prevented%20from%20entering%20the%20barricaded%20area%20of%20the%20mosque%20after%20December%201993.%20The%20rag-bhog%20and%20sanskar%20rituals%20were%20also%20stopped%2C%20Pathak%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20ancient%20Hindu%20idols%20and%20several%20other%20religious%20items%20linked%20to%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20were%20inside%20the%20cellar.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20carry%20out%20regular%20puja%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emurtis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(idols)%20inside%20the%20tehkhana%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040843000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04152216%2FUntitled-design-8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgyanvapi-masjid-keshav-prasad-maurya-uma-bharti%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'There%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20their%20lying.%20No%20such%20puja%20has%20ever%20happened%2C'%20the%20mosque%20authorities%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgyanvapi-masjid-keshav-prasad-maurya-uma-bharti%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20seeks%20greater%20market%20access%20for%20steel%2C%20rice%2C%20shrimp%20from%20S%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040411000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-01%2F01%2Ffull%2F1704085323-5961.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-seeks-greater-market-access-for-steel-rice-shrimp-from-s-korea-124020400297_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22These%20are%20part%20of%20the%20negotiations%2C%20which%20are%20underway%2C%20for%20the%20upgradation%20of%20the%20existing%20free%20trade%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20which%20is%20officially%20dubbed%20as%20CEPA%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-seeks-greater-market-access-for-steel-rice-shrimp-from-s-korea-124020400297_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Findia-seeks-greater-market-access-for-steel-rice-shrimp-from-s-korea-124020400297_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Findia-seeks-greater-market-access-for-steel-rice-shrimp-from-s-korea-124020400297_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MLA's%20Big%20Remarks%20On%20Hemant%20Soren%20Ahead%20Of%20Jharkhand%20Majority%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere's%20many%20a%20slip%20'twixt%20the%20cup%20and%20the%20lip.%20This%20proverb%20holds%20true%20for%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Champai%20Soren%20has%20claimed%20the%20support%20of%2047%20MLAs%20of%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD%20and%20taken%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20Tomorrow%2C%20he%20faces%20a%20majority%20test%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20and%20latest%20developments%20indicate%20the%20battle%20is%20far%20from%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2047%20MLAs%2C%20one%20has%20come%20out%20strongly%20against%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20whose%20resignation%20set%20off%20the%20process%20for%20a%20new%20government%20formation.%20Another%20JMM%20legislator%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20is%20off%20the%20grid%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20skip%20the%20floor%20test%20tomorrow.%20The%20JMM%2C%20busy%20keeping%20its%20flock%20of%20MLAs%20together%2C%20has%20stressed%20that%20it%20has%20adequate%20numbers%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20the%2081-member%20Assembly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20JMM%20MLA%20today%20said%20Hemant%20Soren%20had%20ignored%20his%20advice%20and%20that%20landed%20him%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELobin%20Hembrom%2C%20who%20represents%20Borio%20seat%20in%20Sahibganj%20district%2C%20was%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20a%20non-political%20organisation.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20media%20on%20the%20sidelines%2C%20Mr%20Hembrom%20said%20the%20JMM%20manifesto%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20state%20polls%20had%20promised%20the%20implementation%20of%20Chota%20Nagpur%20Tenancy%20Act%20and%20Santhal%20Parganas%20Tenancy%20Act.%20The%20JMM%20MLA%20also%20said%20the%20central%20law%2C%20Panchayat%20(Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas)%C2%A0Act%2C%201996%2C%20has%20not%20been%20implemented%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20two%20laws%20are%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20land%20rights%20of%20tribals%2C%20the%20PESA%20Act%20empowers%20the%20gram%20sabha%20to%20protect%20tribals%20from%20exploitation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20gram%20sabha%20has%20no%20power%20now.%20If%20the%20PESA%20Act%20was%20implemented%2C%20it%20would%20be%20more%20powerful.%20When%20none%20of%20these%20shields%20(for%20tribals)%20was%20implemented%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20form%20this%20forum%2C%20Jharkhand%20Bachao%20Morcha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislator%20said%20he%20would%20sever%20all%20ties%20from%20JMM.%20%26quot%3BJharkhand%20was%20formed%20after%20such%20a%20struggle%20under%20Shibu%20Soren.%20But%20even%20today%2C%20these%20issues%20have%20not%20been%20resolved%20at%20the%20ground.%20People%20are%20now%20calling%20me%20a%20traitor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemant%20Soren%2C%20who%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20resigned%20late%20on%20Wednesday.%20Champai%20Soren%20took%20over%20after%20claiming%20support%20of%2047%20MLAs%20from%20JMM%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD.%20He%20needs%20to%20prove%20his%20government's%20majority%20in%20the%20House%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hembrom%20said%20he%20would%20now%20see%20how%20the%20state%20government%20under%20Champai%20Soren%20functions.%20He%20added%20that%20he%20would%20keep%20raising%20these%20issues%20in%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20land%20scam%20allegations%2C%20in%20which%20connection%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20irregularities.%20IAS%20officers%20are%20involved.%20Nobody%20can%20touch%20that%20land.%20This%20means%20that%20CNT%20Act%20is%20not%20in%20force.%20Now%20people%20are%20going%20to%20jail.%20Eventually%2C%20our%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20jail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLA%20said%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Hemant%20Soren%20on%20this%20issue.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20warned%20him%20that%20the%20people%20around%20him%20are%20maligning%20his%20image%20and%20he%20should%20be%20careful.%20He%20replied%20that%20I%20speak%20nonsense%20and%20this%20gives%20an%20opportunity%20to%20the%20Opposition.%20I%20had%20then%20told%20him%20that%20he%20and%20Shibu%20Soren%20are%20my%20leaders%20and%20I%20cannot%20tolerate%20your%20disrespect.%20If%20he%20had%20heeded%20my%20advice%2C%20he%20would%20not%20have%20seen%20this%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hembrom%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20snatched%20the%20land%20of%20tribals%20in%20the%20name%20of%20airport%2C%20dams%20and%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Borio%20MLA%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%20is%20led%20by%20a%20tribal%2C%20but%20run%20by%20non-tribals.%20%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20a%20tribal%20Chief%20Minister.%20We%20got%20one.%20But%20everything%20is%20done%20by%20Biharis.%20I%20have%20raised%20this%20multiple%20times%2C%20but%20Hemant%20Soren%20did%20not%20respond%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJMM%20general%20secretary%20Supriyo%20Bhattacharya%20said%20they%20have%20spoken%20to%20Mr%20Hembrom.%20%26quot%3BHe%20will%20be%20coming%20for%20the%20floor%20test%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20MLA%2C%20Chamra%20Linda%20from%20Bishunpur%20constituency%2C%20cannot%20be%20contacted%2C%20it%20is%20learnt.%20Mr%20Linda%20was%20also%20absent%20at%20party%20meetings%20held%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20majority%20test.%20While%20JMM%20leaders%20said%20he%20was%20unwell%2C%20sources%20revealed%20that%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20failed%20to%20contact%20the%20legislator.%20Earlier%2C%20Mr%20Linda%20too%20had%20attacked%20the%20JMM%20government%20and%20said%20it%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20firm%20step%20for%20tribal%20welfare%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707040140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F3udg0i38_hemant-soren-lobin-hembrom_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-floor-test-hemant-soren-champai-soren-hemant-soren-ignored-advice-jharkhand-mla-ahead-of-crucial-floor-test-4991491%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There's%20many%20a%20slip%20'twixt%20the%20cup%20and%20the%20lip.%20This%20proverb%20holds%20true%20for%20the%20current%20situation%20in%20Jharkhand.%20Champai%20Soren%20has%20claimed%20the%20support%20of%2047%20MLAs%20of%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%2C%20Congress%20and%20RJD%20and%20taken%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-floor-test-hemant-soren-champai-soren-hemant-soren-ignored-advice-jharkhand-mla-ahead-of-crucial-floor-test-4991491%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-floor-test-hemant-soren-champai-soren-hemant-soren-ignored-advice-jharkhand-mla-ahead-of-crucial-floor-test-4991491%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjharkhand-floor-test-hemant-soren-champai-soren-hemant-soren-ignored-advice-jharkhand-mla-ahead-of-crucial-floor-test-4991491%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Term%20'EVM'%20No%20Longer%20Serves%20Us.%20We%20Need%20to%20Understand%20'Electronic%20Voting%20Systems'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150142%2FF-O786RagAAWr6B.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20an%20observer%20of%20the%20electoral%20system%20in%20the%20country%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20have%20attended%20meetings%20in%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20as%20a%20member%20of%20civil%20society%20in%20the%20early%20days%20when%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20were%20first%20used%20on%20a%20large%20scale.%20Many%20then%20pointed%20out%20to%20the%20ECI%20that%20while%20the%20machines%20were%20fine%20as%20they%20were%2C%20the%20issue%20of%20major%20concern%20was%20the%20voter-machine%20interaction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBack%20then%20it%20was%20a%20challenge%20to%20get%20voters%20who%20were%20not%20tech%20savvy%20%E2%80%93%20and%20there%20are%20still%20many%20%E2%80%93%20to%20use%20the%20EVMs%20properly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20of%20water%20has%20flown%20down%20the%20Ganga%20since%20then%20and%20now%20EVMs%20are%20here%20to%20stay.%20There%20are%20however%20ever-increasing%20doubts%20about%20the%20reliability%20and%20dependability%20of%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20has%20been%20written%20and%20said%20about%20this%20issue.%20Having%20followed%20that%2C%20I%20had%20decided%20quite%20some%20time%20ago%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20new%20that%20can%20be%20said%2C%20so%20I%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20I%20have%20recently%20come%20across%20a%20few%20prominent%20comments%20which%20prompt%20me%20to%20comment%20on%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEVS%20vs%20EVM%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20issue%20is%20of%20terminology%20and%20it%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20simply%20using%20one%20word%20or%20expression%20in%20place%20of%20another.%20In%20this%20case%20it%20reflects%20a%20mindset.%20When%20the%20EVMs%20were%20first%20introduced%2C%20the%20most%20important%20feature%20was%20claimed%20to%20be%20that%20these%20were%20what%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Cstand-alone%E2%80%9D%20machines%20which%20could%20not%20be%20connected%20with%20or%20contacted%20by%20any%20external%20source%20or%20device.%20And%20indeed%2C%20they%20are.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20ever%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%2C%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20stand-alone%20EVM%20but%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20comprising%20of%20an%20EVM%2C%20a%20VVPAT%20machine%2C%20and%20a%20Control%20Unit.%20These%20three%20machines%20thus%20constitute%20a%20system%20which%20correctly%20should%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20an%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EElectronic%20Voting%20System%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(EVS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20EVS%20is%20no%20longer%20stand-alone%20because%20the%20VVPAT%20machines%20have%20to%20be%20provided%20additional%20information%20by%20connecting%20these%20to%20external%20devices%20(laptops)%20which%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20part%20of%20the%20EVS.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFocusing%20the%20entire%20discussion%20using%20the%20term%20EVMs%20to%20actually%20refer%20to%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20tends%20to%20confuse%20a%20lot%20of%20lay%20voters%20who%20still%20think%20that%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20is%20being%20discussed.%20The%20only%20people%20who%20possibly%20like%20this%20confusion%20are%20those%20who%20may%20benefit%20from%20it%20and%20let%20the%20status%20quo%20continue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMore%20technology%20versus%20simplicity%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20plethora%20of%20solutions%20and%20resolutions%20of%20the%20issue%20have%20been%20suggested%20over%20the%20years.%20A%20common%20feature%20of%20almost%20all%20suggested%20solutions%20is%20more%20and%20more%20dependence%20on%20technology.%20As%20a%20matter%20of%20fact%2C%20this%20piece%20has%20been%20prompted%20by%20the%20interview%20of%20a%20technical%20expert%20that%20I%20saw%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fz5Y6z29El3I%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22EVMs%20Can%20Be%20Manipulated%2C%20Not%20Hacked%2C%20But%20There's%20a%20Simple%2C%20Straightforward%2C%20Inexpensive%20Remedy%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETechnology%20focused%20solutions%20follow%20the%20general%20belief%20that%20all%20problems%20can%20be%20solved%20with%20increasing%20use%20of%20more%20sophisticated%20technology.%20This%20is%20indeed%20true%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20situations%20but%20not%20necessarily%20true%20in%20all%20situations.%20The%20situation%20of%20electronic%20voting%20in%20India%20seems%20to%20be%20one%20such.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuggested%20solution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20that%20a%20significant%2C%20if%20not%20large%2C%20proportion%20of%20voters%20in%20India%20are%20not%20fully%20literate%20and%20not%20very%20tech%20savvy%20(it%20needs%20to%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20using%20a%20simple%20or%20%E2%80%98smart%E2%80%99%20cell%20phone%20does%20not%20make%20one%20necessarily%20tech-savvy)%2C%20I%20propose%20that%20we%20use%20the%20simplest%20technology%20possible%20for%20this%20purpose.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20is%20outlined%20below%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20EVMs%20have%20been%20in%20use%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20and%20voters%20in%20general%20are%20familiar%20with%20their%20use%2C%20EVMs%20should%20be%20retained.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20VVPATs%20and%20Control%20Units%20should%20be%20removed%2C%20and%20replaced%20by%20a%20simple%20printer%20capable%20of%20printing%20a%20slip%20showing%20(a)%20the%20name%20and%20party%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20that%20the%20voter%20voted%20for%20and%20(b)%20a%20bar%20code%20which%20enables%20machine%20counting%20of%20the%20slips.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20on%20which%20the%20above%20information%20is%20printed%20should%20be%20of%20good%20and%20durable%20quality%20capable%20of%20retaining%20the%20printed%20information%20for%20seven%20years%20(as%20opposed%20to%20the%20current%20paper%20from%20which%20the%20printed%20matter%20reportedly%20disappears%20after%20a%20rather%20short%20time).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voter%20should%20be%20able%20to%20collect%20the%20slip%20from%20the%20printer%20directly%20(without%20any%20election%20official%20having%20to%20intervene%20or%20assist%20the%20voter%20in%20any%20way)%2C%20and%20place%20the%20slip%20directly%20in%20a%20common%20ballot%20box.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20slips%20in%20the%20common%20ballot%20box%20should%20be%20machine-counted%20based%20on%20the%20bar%20code%20printed%20on%20each%20slip.%20This%20counting%20process%20using%20counting%20machines%20based%20on%20the%20bar%20code%20should%20not%20take%20many%20days%20as%20apprehended%20by%20the%20ECI%20whenever%20a%20demand%20for%20a%20hundred%20percent%20counting%20of%20VVPAT%20slips%20is%20made%2C%20and%20in%20which%20even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20had%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20proposal%20bypasses%20all%20complications%20and%20suspicions%20that%20have%20arisen%20about%20the%20VVPATs.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20restate%20them%20here%20because%20they%20have%20been%20stated%20repeatedly.%20The%20only%20additional%20requirements%20are%20good%20quality%20paper%20and%20ink%20so%20that%20the%20printing%20lasts%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20a%20barcode-based%20counting%20machine.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20system%20will%20need%20some%20fine%20tuning%20and%20there%20are%20many%20experts%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20sure%20a%20country%20which%20has%20landed%20a%20vehicle%20on%20the%20moon%20can%20produce%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJagdeep%20S.%20Chhokar%20is%20a%20concerned%20citizen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707039241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04150142%2FF-O786RagAAWr6B.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Focusing%20the%20entire%20discussion%20using%20the%20term%20EVMs%20to%20actually%20refer%20to%20a%20group%20of%20three%20machines%20tends%20to%20confuse%20a%20lot%20of%20lay%20voters%20who%20still%20think%20that%20the%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machine%20is%20being%20discussed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-voting-machine-election-polls%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Embassy%20Worker%20Arrested%20For%20Spying%20Was%20Providing%20Army%20Info%20To%20Pak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS)%20has%20arrested%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20for%20allegedly%20spying%20for%20Pakistan's%20intelligence%20agency%20ISI.%20He%20was%20arrested%20in%20Meerut.%20The%20arrested%20individual%2C%20identified%20as%20Satendra%20Siwal%2C%20was%20working%20as%20a%20Multi-Tasking%20Staff%20(MTS)%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20unfolded%20as%20ATS%20received%20intelligence%20from%20confidential%20sources%20suggesting%20that%20ISI%20handlers%20were%20luring%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20employees%2C%20offering%20financial%20incentives%20in%20exchange%20for%20sensitive%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20The%20information%20being%20exchanged%20posed%20a%20grave%20threat%20to%20India's%20internal%20and%20external%20security%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatendra%20Siwal%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Shahmahiuddinpur%20village%20in%20Hapur%2C%20was%20identified%20as%20a%20key%20player%20in%20this%20espionage%20network.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20extracting%20confidential%20documents%20by%20exploiting%20his%20position%20within%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow.%20The%20accused%2C%20motivated%20by%20greed%20for%20money%2C%20allegedly%20passed%20critical%20information%20concerning%20the%20strategic%20activities%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Indian%20military%20establishments%20to%20ISI%20handlers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ATS%20was%20receiving%20intelligence%20from%20various%20confidential%20sources%20that%20the%20handlers%20of%20the%20Pakistani%20intelligence%20agency%20ISI%2C%20through%20some%20persons%2C%20were%20luring%20the%20employees%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20with%20money%20to%20obtain%20strategically%20and%20strategically%20important%20information%20related%20to%20the%20Indian%20Army%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20pose%20a%20huge%20threat%20to%20the%20internal%20and%20external%20security%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20extensive%20intelligence%20gathering%20and%20surveillance%2C%20Satendra%20Siwal%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20ATS%20Field%20Unit%20in%20Meerut%20for%20interrogation.%20During%20questioning%2C%20he%20reportedly%20failed%20to%20provide%20satisfactory%20answers%2C%20eventually%20confessing%20to%20his%20involvement%20in%20spy%20activities.%20Satendra%20Siwal%20has%20been%20working%20as%20an%20India%20Based%20Security%20Assistant%20(IBSA)%20at%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20since%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20Siwal%20under%20sections%20of%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country%20and%20also%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20that%20it%20is%20aware%20of%20Satendra%20Siwal's%20arrest%20and%20is%20working%20with%20the%20investigative%20authorities%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707038820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ffgc40er8_satendra-siwal_625x300_04_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-embassy-employee-posted-in-moscow-arrested-for-spying-for-pakistan-4991189%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20has%20arrested%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%2C%20Russia%2C%20on%20charges%20of%20spying%20for%20Pakistan's%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20ISI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-embassy-employee-posted-in-moscow-arrested-for-spying-for-pakistan-4991189%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-embassy-employee-posted-in-moscow-arrested-for-spying-for-pakistan-4991189%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findian-embassy-employee-posted-in-moscow-arrested-for-spying-for-pakistan-4991189%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chile%20wildfires%3A%2099%20dead%20as%20wildfire%20tears%20through%20Valparaiso%20region%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707038377000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F13532%2Fproduction%2F_132545197_p0h8ys84.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68197170%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Officials%20have%20warned%20the%20death%20toll%20is%20likely%20to%20rise%20as%20rescue%20teams%20reach%20the%20hardest%20hit%20areas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A454%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-latin-america-68197170%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20least%2028%20killed%20in%20shelling%20at%20bakery%20in%20Russian-occupied%20city%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20Moscow-installed%20officials%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707037680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-russia-ukraine-lysychansk_6443915.jpg%3F20240204100308%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-least-28-killed-in-shelling-at-bakery-in-russian-occupied-city-in-eastern-ukraine-moscow-installed-officials-say-13063815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2028%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20shelling%20at%20a%20bakery%20in%20the%20Russian-occupied%20city%20of%20Lysychansk%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20Moscow-installed%20officials%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A138%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fat-least-28-killed-in-shelling-at-bakery-in-russian-occupied-city-in-eastern-ukraine-moscow-installed-officials-say-13063815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ahead%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20EC%20Answers%20Longstanding%20Query%20on%20How%20EVMs%20Get%20Signals%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04142329%2FF_r3Z09a8AAxnSm.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20has%20updated%20on%20January%2030%2C%20the%20list%20of%20frequently%20asked%20questions%20(FAQ)%20on%20its%20website%2C%20in%20which%20it%20has%20addressed%20how%20signals%20are%20received%20and%20sent%20between%20the%20EVM%20(electronic%20voting%20machines)%20and%20VVPAT%20(voter%20verified%20paper%20audit%20trails).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FAQs%20come%20as%20opposition%20parties%20have%20raised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fjairam-ramesh-evm-concerns-chief-election-commissioner-letter-ec-9091381%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20questions%20about%20the%20role%20of%20EVMs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eci.gov.in%2Fevm-faq-new%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EQuestion%2086%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20FAQs%20answers%20how%20signal%20or%20command%20flow%20between%20various%20units%20of%20EVM%20i.e.%20between%20ballot%20unit%20(BU)%2C%20control%20unit%20(CU)%20and%20VVVPAT.%20It%20also%20answers%20if%20the%20VVPAT%20which%20is%20kept%20along%20with%20BU%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment%20of%20the%20voter%20receives%20any%20signal%20or%20command%20from%20BU%20and%20vice-versa.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20has%20stated%20in%20its%20answer%20that%20in%20M3%20EVMs%20(the%20current%20model%20that%20is%20being%20used)%2C%20the%20CU%20acts%20as%20the%20Master%20%E2%80%9Cirrespective%20of%20the%20position%20in%20which%20it%20is%20placed%20or%20connected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBU%20and%20VVPAT%20act%20as%20Slave%20units%20in%20the%20connected%20network%2C%20which%20receive%20commands%20from%20CU%20to%20act%20as%20per%20the%20application%20programme.%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20do%20not%20communicate%20with%20each%20other.%20It%20is%20the%20CU%20that%20communicates%20with%20both%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%20When%20a%20voter%20presses%20a%20candidate%20button%20on%20BU%2C%20the%20BU%20sends%20the%20button%20number%20to%20CU%20and%20in%20turn%2C%20the%20CU%20communicates%20to%20VVPAT%20to%20print%20the%20slip%20of%20the%20corresponding%20button%20number.%20Only%20after%20printing%20and%20cutting%20of%20the%20printed%20VVPAT%20slip%2C%20the%20CU%20registers%20the%20vote%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20website%20shows%20a%20diagram%20to%20explain%20the%20signal%20flow%20details%20int%20he%20M3%20model%20EV-VVPAT.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20states%20that%20in%20the%20M3%20model%2C%E2%80%9DMaster-Slave%20bus%20architecture%20is%20used.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20this%20model%20the%20VVPAT%20can%20be%20connected%20anywhere%20in%20the%20EVM%20M3%20bus.%20The%20Control%20Unit%20(CU)%20implements%20communication%2C%20command%20processing%2C%20handling%20of%20key%20operations%20and%20handling%20of%20all%20the%20commands%2Fresponses%20to%2Ffrom%20BU%20and%20VVPAT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCommunication%20on%20the%20bus%20is%20initiated%20by%20the%20%E2%80%9CMaster%E2%80%9D%20(CU)%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9CCommand%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9CSlave%E2%80%9D%20(BU%20%26amp%3B%20VVPAT).%20The%20%E2%80%98Slave%E2%80%99%20which%20is%20constantly%20monitoring%20the%20bus%20for%20%E2%80%9CCommands%E2%80%9D%20will%20recognise%20only%20the%20%E2%80%98Commands%E2%80%99%20addressed%20to%20it%20and%20will%20respond%20by%20performing%20an%20action%20and%20by%20returning%20a%20%E2%80%98Response%E2%80%99.%20Only%20the%20Master%20can%20initiate%20a%20command.%20CU%20is%20always%20the%20Master%20in%20the%20ECI%20M3%20EVM%20system%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20in%202021%2C%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Felection-commissions-evms-are-standalone-machines-cant-be-tampered-with-says-expert-committee-2064267.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EECI%E2%80%99s%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20EVMs%20are%20stand-alone%20machines%20which%20are%20neither%20accessible%20remotely%20from%20any%20network%20nor%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20external%20devices.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPAT%2C%20these%20claims%20do%20not%20hold%20as%20these%20machines%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnaukarshah%2Fstatus%2F1360584934159749124%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eapparently%20connected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20laptops%20or%20symbol%20loading%20units%20(SLUs).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20connecting%20an%20external%20device%20to%20EVM-VVPAT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ea)%20after%20announcement%20of%20election%20date%3Cbr%3E%5Cnb)%20after%20publication%20of%20candidate%20list%3Cbr%3E%5Cnc)%20after%20both%20stages%20of%20randomisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20more%20stand-alone%2C%20no%20more%20a%20calculator%20%26amp%3B%20none%20of%20the%20process%20safeguards%20are%20effective%20anymore.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FECISVEEP%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ECISVEEP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20(%40naukarshah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnaukarshah%2Fstatus%2F1377225206993887239%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2031%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3EVVPATs%20were%20inducted%20into%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%202013%20to%20provide%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20scrutiny%20against%20possible%20EVM%20manipulation.%20They%20allow%20physical%20tallying%20of%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopinathan%20said%20that%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20VVPAT%20mechanism%2C%20the%20voting%20process%20became%20%E2%80%9Cvulnerable%20and%20suspicious%E2%80%9D%20instead%20of%20being%20strengthened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20that%20EVMs%20are%20not%20stand-alone%20machines%20as%20they%20are%20connected%20to%20laptops%20of%20SLUs%20and%20it%20is%20not%20single%20programmable%20as%20they%20are%20showing%20names%20and%20symbols%20of%20candidates.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20do%20you%20store%20it%3F%20You%20need%20a%20programmable%20memory.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20stand%20alone%20machine%20and%20it%20has%20a%20programmable%20memory%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20every%20aspect%20of%20a%20full%20fledged%20computer%20apart%20from%20a%20screen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Logical%20Indian.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGopinathan%2C%20who%20was%20the%20returning%20officer%20for%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20subsequently%20stepped%20down%20as%20an%20IAS%20officer%20over%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20the%20following%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Felection-commission-of-india-addresses-5-year-old-query-on-electronic-voting-machines-ahead-of-lok-sabha-elections%2Fcid%2F1998185%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Telegraph%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Gopinathan%20said%20that%20while%20he%20has%20not%20examined%20the%20poll%20panel%E2%80%99s%20FAQ%2C%20the%20current%20process%20does%20not%20fulfil%20the%20demands%20of%20a%20fair%20election.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20fair%20election%20is%20one%20where%20the%20voter%20has%20agency%20to%20verify%20the%20vote%2C%20and%20the%20candidate%20can%20verify%20counting.%20The%20current%20process%20fulfills%20neither.%20Verification%20would%20mean%20the%20ability%20to%20accept%20or%20reject%20what%20is%20registered%20on%20the%20VVPAT%20slip%20that%20one%20sees%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%20say%20that%20in%20case%20of%20a%20mismatch%20between%20the%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%20vote%20tallies%20(five%20are%20tallied%20in%20every%20Assembly%20segment)%2C%20the%20latter%20is%20to%20be%20counted%20for%20that%20machine.%20Thus%2C%20the%20EC%20itself%20considers%20the%20VVPAT%20more%20reliable%20than%20the%20CU.%20Then%20why%20does%20it%20rely%20on%20the%20CU%20count%20for%20the%20overall%20result%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707036852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F04142329%2FF_r3Z09a8AAxnSm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-election-commission-lok-sabha-faq-signal-kannan-gopinathan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202021%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Kannan%20Gopinathan%20raised%20serious%20questions%20over%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20EVMs%20are%20stand-alone%20machines%20which%20are%20neither%20accessible%20remotely%20from%20any%20network%20nor%20can%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20external%20devices%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fevm-election-commission-lok-sabha-faq-signal-kannan-gopinathan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Ministry%20Cancels%20Christian%20Organisation's%20FCRA%20Licence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F24214119%2Fmha.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20long%20list%20of%20cancellations%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20on%20February%203%2C%20cancelled%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%20registration%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Social%20Service%20Society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20society%2C%20abbreviated%20as%20TNSOSS%2C%20is%20a%20Christian%20non-governmental%20organisation%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Catholic%20Bishops%20Conference.%20The%20Union%20government%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20TNSOSS%20had%20violated%20FCRA%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Christian%20association%20the%20FCRA%20registration%20of%20which%20has%20been%20cancelled%20in%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu-social-service-organisation-loses-fcra-registration%2Farticle67808370.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20The%20other%20one%20was%20the%20World%20Vision%20India%2C%20which%20lost%20its%20licence%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20that%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20also%20cancelled%20the%20licence%20of%20the%20New%20Delhi-based%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20Research%20(CPR)%2C%20a%20public%20policy%20think%20tank.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20organisation%20Yamini%20Aiyar%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministry-cancels-centre-for-policy-researchs-fcra-registration%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20basis%20of%20this%20decision%20%E2%80%9Cincomprehensible%20and%20disproportionate%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20a%20series%20of%20amendments%20to%20the%20FCRA%2C%20successive%20governments%20had%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20activities%20of%20several%20NGOs%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20face%20several%20challenges%20including%20a%20loss%20of%20jobs.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20concerns%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20using%20the%20FCRA%20to%20curb%20the%20activities%20of%20NGOs%20that%20are%20critical%20of%20it%20have%20been%20raised%20in%20the%20back%20of%20thousands%20of%20licence%20cancellations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu-social-service-organisation-loses-fcra-registration%2Farticle67808370.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%20since%202011%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20has%20cancelled%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20NGOs%E2%80%99%20registrations%2C%20citing%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707036382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F24214119%2Fmha.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-home-ministry-cancels-christian-organisations-fcra-licence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20is%20the%20second%20Tamil%20Nadu-based%20Christian%20association%20the%20FCRA%20registration%20of%20which%20has%