tember%208%2C%20when%20it%20took%20about%2034%20minutes%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%2010%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelhi%2C%20Mumbai%20Also%20Hit%20By%20Traffic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20(44)%20and%20Mumbai%20(52)%20were%20also%20on%20the%20TomTom%20Traffic%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20on%20average%2C%20it%20took%2021%20minutes%2040%20seconds%20to%20drive%2010%20km%20in%202023%2C%20and%2021%20minutes%2020%20seconds%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20report%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%2C%20Dublin%2C%20Toronto%20Worst%20Traffic-Hit%20Cities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELondon%2C%20with%20an%20average%20travel%20time%20per%2010%20km%20of%2037%20minutes%2C%20was%20the%20city%20worst%20affected%20by%20traffic%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20the%20TomTom%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDublin%20had%20an%20average%20travel%20time%20per%2010%20km%20of%2029%20minutes%2030%20seconds%20last%20year%20and%20was%20ranked%20second%20on%20the%20list%2C%20while%20Toronto%20in%20Canada%2C%C2%A0where%20it%20took%2029%20minutes%20to%20travel%2010%20km%2C%20was%20named%20third.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20London%20and%20Dublin%2C%20travel%20times%20for%20around%20a%209-km%20journey%20increased%20by%20%2B1%20minute%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAverage%20Speed%20Decreased%20In%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20average%20speed%20decreased%20in%20228%20of%20the%20387%20cities%20analyzed%20in%20the%20traffic%20index%2C%20compared%20to%202022%2C%20TomTom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%2082%20cities%20saw%20their%20average%20speed%20remain%20unchanged%2C%20while%2077%20cities%20had%20a%20higher%20average%20speed%20and%20shorter%20journey%20times%20than%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20more%20than%2060%25%20of%20351%20cities%20where%20TomTom%20aggregated%20fuel%20prices%2C%20the%20average%20budget%20in%20fuel%20increased%20by%2015%25%