p%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706855405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340584%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Karnataka's%20Suresh%20S%20R%20and%20his%20wife%20Maithili%20started%20Bhoomi%20Agri%20Ventures%20to%20turn%20areca%20palm%20leaves%20and%20husk%20into%20eco-friendly%20vegan%20leather.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A49%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Was%20Abused%20as%20a%2013-YO%20%26amp%3B%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20Parents%20Should%20Learn%20About%20Childhood%20Trauma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20Warning%3A%20Mentions%20of%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20violence%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20eating%20disorders%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20human%20existence%2C%20our%20experiences%20shape%20us.%20The%20personality%20formed%20in%20our%20formative%20years%20is%20a%20gift%20from%20those%20we%20encounter%2C%20leaving%20lasting%20impressions.%20When%20these%20experiences%20involve%20abuse%20and%20violence%2C%20they%20penetrate%20deep%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20essence.%20Such%20memories%20can%20hinder%20emotional%20growth%2C%20trapping%20individuals%20in%20cycles%20of%20fear%20and%20self-doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2043%2C%20Mansi%20Poddar%20still%20wrestles%20with%20the%20traumas%20of%20her%20early%20life%2C%20haunting%20her%20and%20leading%20to%20toxic%20cycles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20endured%20a%20troubled%20early%20life%20filled%20with%20abuse%20and%20violence.%20I%20had%20no%20one%20to%20turn%20to%20back%20then.%20As%20part%20of%20my%20healing%20process%2C%20I%20am%20working%20towards%20creating%20an%20ecosystem%20where%20no%20one%20feels%20unheard%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20a%20psychotherapist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Heal%20Grow%20Thrive%20Foundation%2C%20Mansi%20engages%20in%20heartfelt