fforts%20to%20overcome%20challenges%20hindering%20SDG%20progress%20in%20India.%20The%20conclave%2C%20focusing%20on%20sustainability%2C%20digital%20equity%2C%20and%20social%20innovation%2C%20highlighted%20collaborative%20partnerships%20for%20SDG%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340504%2Fnasscom-foundation-techforgood-conclave-new-delhi-achieve-sdg-success-digital-india%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IAS%20Officer%20Uses%20IoT%20to%20Raise%20Water%20Supply%2C%20Cut%20Power%20Bills%20by%2040%25%20in%2016%20Villages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EErode%20district%2C%20which%20lies%20in%20the%20western%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289205%2Frainwater-harvesting-system-in-tamil-nadu-helps-village-during-cyclone%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20region%20characterised%20by%20limited%20rainfall%2C%20dry%20climate%20and%20erratic%20water%20supply.%20For%20the%20approximately%2011%20lakh%20residents%20of%20the%20district%20who%20reside%20in%20its%20rural%20areas%20(as%20per%202011%20Census)%2C%20this%20irregular%20water%20supply%20is%20an%20even%20bigger%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20while%20the%20rural%20water%20demand%20in%20the%20district%20is%2074%20MLD%20(million%20litres%20a%20day)%2C%20the%20water%20supplied%20is%20approximately%2040%20to%2055%20LPCD%20(litres%20per%20capita%20per%20day).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20water%20is%20supplied%20from%20the%20Kaveri%20and%20Bhavani%20rivers%20through%2020%20Combined%20Water%20Supply%20Schemes%20(i.e.%20water%20from%20rivers)%20apart%20from%20local%20borewell%20sources.%20Currently%2C%20most%20villages%20in%20Erode%20district%20and%20elsewhere%20rely%20on%20overhead%20tanks%20(OHTs)%20for%20their%20water%20supply%2C%20sourced%20either%20from%20borewells%20or%20infiltration%20wells%20in%20nearby%20rivers%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20District%20Collector%20(DC)%20Raja%20Gopal%20Sunkara%2C%20a%202015-batch%20IAS%20officer%2C%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC%20Sunkara%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20in%20the%20Erode%20district%2C%20there%20are%20over%204%2C700%20Over%20Head%20Tanks%20(OHTs)%20in%20rural%20areas%20whereas%20the%20number%20of%20tank%20operators%20is%20only%20299.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20reliance%20on%20tank%20operators%2C%20he%20explains%20the%20following%20problems%20were%20being%20faced%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%20High%20water%20losses%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20villages%2C%20we%20see%20overflowing%20OHTs%20since%20the%20motors%20are%20not%20switched%20off%20on%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20DC%20Sunkara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%20Unreliable%20timings%20of%20water%20supply%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Since%20tank%20operators%20have%20to%20manually%20manage%20OHTs%2C%20water%20supply%20timings%20change%20from%20day%20to%20day%20depending%20on%20their%20availability%20and%20punctuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%20High%20electricity%20bill%20for%20the%20local%20body%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20motors%20are%20not%20switched%20off%20on%20time%2C%20the%20electricity%20bills%20of%20villages%20increase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%20Dry%20Run%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Motors%20get%20damaged%20when%20they%20are%20run%20without%20water%20in%20the%20sump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20K%20Renuva%20Devi%2C%20the%20Panchayat%20president%20of%20Kuttapalayam%20village%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20were%20dependent%20on%20the%20tank%20operator%2C%20who%20used%20to%20manually%20operate%20the%20gate%20valves%20and%20motor%20pumps.%20There%20used%20to%20be%20overflow%20from%20the%20tanks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20these%20failings%20of%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system%20in%20Erode%20district%2C%20DC%20Sunkara%20has%20installed%20IoT%20devices%20in%2050%20habitations%20across%2016%20villages%2C%20which%20the%20district%20administration%20claims%20have%20not%20only%20reduced%20electricity%20bills%20by%20approximately%2040%25%20but%20also%20increased%20water%20supply%20by%20over%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22DC%20Raja%20Gopal%20Sunkara's%20decision%20to%20employ%20IoT%20has%20addressed%20key%20concerns%20associated%20with%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-21-at-17.08.23-1-1706793443-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340518%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDC%20Raja%20Gopal%20Sunkara%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20employ%20IoT%20has%20addressed%20key%20concerns%20associated%20with%20the%20OHT%20water%20supply%20system.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%