%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20it%20was%20not%20one%20place%20that%20could%20help%20me%20but%20a%20lot.%20Visiting%20various%20schools%20was%20a%20great%20learning%20arc%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20five%20senses%20to%20navigate%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20school%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20navigated%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20senses%3A%20sight%2C%20hearing%2C%20touch%2C%20and%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%2015%25%20of%20people%20with%20blindness%20experience%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20sight.%20The%20majority%20of%20individuals%20who%20are%20blind%20may%20perceive%20light%20or%20colour%2C%20and%20those%20with%20different%20impairments%20have%20varying%20degrees%20of%20usable%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20walls%20have%20different%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20recognise%20the%20classes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-4-1706623360-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340122%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20walls%20have%20different%20textures%20for%20students%20to%20recognise