%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340126%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20are%20five%20special%20classrooms%20and%20seven%20classrooms%20with%20individual%20courtyards%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20explained%20that%20he%20planted%20the%20shrubs%20to%20attract%20butterflies%20and%20birds%2C%20and%20to%20diversify%20and%20improve%20the%20natural%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20traditional%20rainwater%20harvesting%20technique%20known%20as%20Khambhati%20Kuva%20(Percolation%20well)%20was%20implemented.%20The%20well%2C%20with%20a%20diameter%20of%2010%20feet%20and%20a%20depth%20of%2030%20feet%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20collect%20rainwater%20and%20recharge%20the%20ground.%20This%20well%20can%20absorb%2045%2C000%20to%2060%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%20in%20just%20one%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20and%20running%20since%202021%2C%20Anand%20says%20looking%20back%20at%20his%20work%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20professional%2C%20I%20approach%20all%20projects%20with%20the%20same%20intensity.%20However%2C%20working%20on%20this%20project%20was%20unique.%20In%20our%20architectural%20education%2C%20we%20had%20never%20delved%20into%20questions%20about%20users%20to%20this%20extent.%20It%20opened%20my%20eyes%20to%20the%20realisation%20that%20in%20designing%20any%20building%2C%20be%20it%20public%20structures%20or%20entire%20cities%2C%20we%2