0It%20takes%20a%20little%20time%20for%20me%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20operate%20a%20camera%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20reels%20I%E2%80%99ve%20posted%20on%20IG%20have%20been%20shot%20in%20my%20village%20and%20on%20my%20Motorola%20Moto%20G40%20smartphone.%20However%2C%20in%20making%20these%20reels%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20broken%20the%20screen%20but%20decided%20to%20not%20change%20or%20replace%20it%20since%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20I%20will%20buy%20a%20new%20phone%20once%20I%20have%20the%20money%20for%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20negativity%20%26amp%3B%20fame%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20Dhiraj%20Takri%20started%20making%20reels%2C%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20getting%20a%20single%20comment.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20first%20video%20went%20viral%2C%20he%20received%20many%20hateful%20and%20tasteless%20comments%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20also%20went%20on%20for%20only%20a%20week%20or%20two.%20Once%20my%20other%20videos%20started%20to%20go%20viral%2C%20even%20the%20negative%20comments%20trickled%20down.%20Even%20those%20who%20called%20me%20all%20sorts%20of%20things%20under%20the%20sun%20were%20now%20telling%20me%20%E2%80%98Why%20are%20you%20looking%20for%20negative%20comments%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dhiraj%20says%20with%20a%20smile.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20his%20family%20or%20fellow%20residents%20in%20Chitrakote%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20safe%20to%20suggest%20that%20no%20one%20expected%20his%20sudden%20rise%20in%20popularity%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20expect%20to%20grow%20at%20this%20rate%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20thankful%20to%20all%20my%20supporters%20who%20like%20and%20share%20my%20reels%20and%20follow%20me%20on%20Instagram%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E