endly%2C%20smart%20and%20made%20of%20floral%20waste%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20is%20available%20in%20three%20variants%20for%20homes%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20cars%2C%20offering%20a%20choice%20of%2015%20fragrances.%20Each%20unit%20is%20equipped%20with%20smart%20sensors%20that%20automatically%20activate%20and%20deactivate%20based%20on%20the%20detection%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20features%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fsustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20body%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20be%20composted%20after%20use%2C%20and%20its%20refills%20are%20organic%20%E2%80%94%20crafted%20from%20temple%20flower%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20nature%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20in%20retaining%20the%20fragrances.%20Chemical%20fresheners%20use%20LPG%20to%20retain%20the%20fragrance.%20We%20use%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20that%20with%20no%20chemicals.%20We%20do%20not%20use%20any%20heat%2C%20water%20vapour%20or%20chemicals%20to%20diffuse%20our%20fragrances.%20We%20use%20our%20own%20Air%20Diffusion%20Technology%20with%20sensors%20to%20diffuse%20aroma%20evenly%20in%20the%20surroundings%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20has%20partnered%20with%20more%20than%2030%20temples%20in%20Jamshedpur%20to%20obtain%20floral%20waste.%20Every%20day%2C%20he%20collects%20a%20minimum%20of%203%20kg%20of%20floral%20waste%20from%20each%20temple.%20To%20date%2C%20he%20has%20recycled%201%2C500%20kg%20of%20temple%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noteworthy%20aspect%20is%20that%20this%20freshener%20is%20safe%20for%20animals%20also.%20Working%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20Animal%20Welfare%20Society%20since%202018%2C%20Rajiv%20was%20shocked%20by%20the%20effects%20of%20human%20behaviour%20on%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rajiv%20made%20wheelchairs%20for%20dogs%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-300x171.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-500x285.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-768x438.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-1536x876.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Falve-1706190156-150x86.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339849%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22913%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERajiv%20made%20%E2%80%98wheelchairs%E2%80%99%20for%20dogs%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20rescue%20cows%20and%20bulls.%20When%20they%20were%20operated%20upon%2C%20veterinarians%20found%20plastic%20in%20their%20stomachs%2C%20which%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20digest.%20I%20have%20been%20against%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fauthor%2Fsowmyamani%2Fpage%2F3%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20that%20day.%20Our%20fresheners%20too%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20plastic%20in%20them.%20Just%20put%20our%20device%20in%20your%20garden%20after%20use%20and%20it%20will%20get%20composted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20the%20startup%20from%20his%20home%20currently%2C%20Rajiv%20hopes%20to%20expand%20soon.%20ALVE%20Green%20Solutions%20has%20collaborated%20with%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Bangalore%2C%20where%20five%20college%20students%20will%20be%20working%20with%20the%20startup%20to%20develop%20the%20product.%20The%20air%20fresheners%20are%20currently%20being%20sold%20offline%2C%20at%20events%2C%20and%20through%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CALVE%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Alveoli%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20sac-like%20structure%20present%20in%20our%20lungs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20exchange%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20and%20oxygen.%20Without%20this%20organ%2C%20the%20body%20fails%20to%20survive%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20most%20important%20part%20of%20our%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20he%20wants%20ALVE%20to%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20each%20home%20for%20healthier%20living.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20create%20products%20that%20not%20only%20meet%20human%20needs%20but%20also%20leave%20a%20positive%20imprint%20on%20our%20planet.%20Our%20vision%20at%20ALVE%20is%20to%20inspire%20a%20world%20where%20fresh%2C%20clean%20air%20is%20not%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20sustainable%20standard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706192933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-21.41.12-2-1706189293.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20ecofriendly%20air%20fresheners%3F%20Jamshedpur's%20Rajiv%20Sharma%20innovated%20ALVE%20smart%20air%20fresheners%20by%20recycling%201500%20kgs%20of%20temple%20flower%20waste.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fja